(1, 'Magic Kingdom Park', 'Disney\'s Magic Kingdom is a theme park located at the Walt Disney World Resort in Orlando, Florida. It is one of the four theme parks within the resort, and it is the first park to be built at the complex, opening its doors in 1971. The Magic Kingdom is a fairytale-themed park, and it has become one of the most famous and recognizable theme parks in the world.\r\n<br><br>\r\nThe Magic Kingdom has seven themed lands, each of which is designed to transport visitors to different fairy tale and fantasy worlds.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<a href=\"#\" style=\"color: black;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:none\">Main Street USA</a> is the first land visitors encounter as they enter the park, and it is designed to resemble a typical small American town from the turn of the 20th century.Visitors can explore this land and take in the sights and sounds of a bygone era, including the iconic Cinderella Castle, which serves as the centerpiece of the park.<br> <br><a href=\"#\" style=\"color: black;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:none\">Adventureland </a>is the next land visitors encounter, and it is designed to transport them to exotic lands such as the Caribbean, Africa, and Asia. Visitors can explore this land and experience attractions such as Pirates of the Caribbean, a classic boat ride through a pirate-filled Caribbean Island, and the Jungle Cruise, a boat ride through the Amazon rainforest. <br><br><a href=\"#\" style=\"color: black;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:none\">Frontierland</a> is a western-themed land that transports visitors to the American Old West. Attractions here include Big Thunder Mountain Railroad, a roller coaster that takes visitors on a wild ride through a western mining town, as well as Frontierland Riverboat Landing, a riverboat ride on the Liberty Belle that offers views of Frontierland and surrounding lands. <br><br><a href=\"#\" style=\"color: black;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:none\">Liberty Square</a> is a colonial-themed land that recreates the atmosphere of colonial America and celebrates the birth of the United States. Visitors can explore this land and take in attractions such as the Hall of Presidents, an audio-animatronic show that features all of the U.S. presidents, and the Haunted Mansion, a spooky tour through a haunted house.<br><br><a href=\"#\" style=\"color: black;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:none\">Fantasyland</a> is the largest of the seven lands, and it is designed to transport visitors to the world of classic Disney fairytales. Attractions here include It\'s a Small World, a boat ride through a world filled with singing animatronics, and Peter Pan\'s Flight, a ride that takes visitors on a magical flight over London.<br><br><a href=\"#\" style=\"color: black;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:none\">Tomorrowland</a> is a futuristic-themed land that takes visitors to a world of innovation and technology. Attractions here include Space Mountain, a roller coaster that takes visitors on a high-speed journey through outer space, and Buzz Lightyear\'s Space Ranger Spin, an interactive ride where visitors help Buzz Lightyear save the universe.<br><br>Finally,<a href=\"#\" style=\"color: black;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:none\"> Mickey\'s Toontown Fair</a> is a cartoon-themed land that takes visitors to the world of classic Disney cartoon characters. Visitors can explore this land and take in attractions such as Mickey\'s Country House, a tour through Mickey Mouse\'s home, and Minnie\'s House, a tour through Minnie Mouse\'s home.<br><br>In addition to the seven themed lands, the Magic Kingdom is home to many parades, shows, and other live performances. The nightly fireworks show, \"Happily Ever After,\" is a highlight of any visit to the park, and it is a stunning display of pyrotechnics that is set against the backdrop of Cinderella Castle.<br><br>Disney\'s Magic Kingdom is a magical and enchanting theme park that is sure to captivate visitors of all ages. Whether you\'re a fan of classic Disney fairytales, futuristic technology, or anything in between, there\'s something for everyone at this iconic park.<br><br>', 'magickingdom/magickingdom1.jpg', 'Magic Kingdom Castle', 'magickingdom/magickingdom2.jpg', 'Chip and Dale waving to the crowd', 'magickingdom/magickingdom3.jpg', 'Partner\'s Statue made of copper of Walt Disney holding hands with Mickey Mouse', 'magickingdom/magickingdom4.jpg', 'Mickey Mouse and Minnie Mouse in the parade', '1180 Seven Seas Drive, Lake Buena Vista, FL 32830', 'https://disneyworld.disney.go.com/destinations/magic-kingdom/', 'magickingdom/magickingdommap.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/Magic+Kingdom+Park/@28.417636,-81.5830477,16.7z/data=!4m5!3m4!1s0x88dd7e536aa54b81:0x66b8bcd58da841a!8m2!3d28.418579!4d-81.5812062', 'Disney\'s Magic Kingdom is a theme park located at the Walt Disney World Resort in Orlando, Florida. It is one of the four theme parks within the resort, and it is the first park to be built at the complex, opening its doors in 1971. The Magic Kingdom is a fairytale-themed park, and it has become one of the most famous and recognizable theme parks in the world. The Magic Kingdom has seven themed lands, each of which is designed to transport visitors to different fairy tale and fantasy worlds.', '109.00', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', ''),
(2, 'EPCOT', 'Epcot is the ultimate destination for a one-of-a-kind travel experience. Located in the heart of Walt Disney World Resort in Orlando, Florida, Epcot offers a unique combination of entertainment, culture, and technology that captures the imagination of visitors of all ages.<br><br>Epcot, which stands for Experimental Prototype Community of Tomorrow, was opened in 1982 as a tribute to the vision of Walt Disney, who wanted to create a futuristic community where people could live, work, and play in harmony. While the original concept was never fully realized, Epcot has become a beloved theme park that celebrates the diversity and innovation of human culture and technology.<br><br>Epcot is divided into two main areas: Future World and World Showcase. Future World is dedicated to science, technology, and innovation, with popular attractions such as Spaceship Earth, Mission: SPACE, and Test Track. Visitors can explore the wonders of the ocean at The Seas with Nemo & Friends, or journey into the imagination at Journey Into Imagination With Figment.<br><br>World Showcase, on the other hand, takes visitors on a tour of eleven different countries, each represented by a pavilion that showcases its culture, cuisine, and traditions. From the enchanting gardens of Japan to the lively streets of Mexico, World Showcase is a feast for the senses, with delicious food, unique shopping, and immersive experiences that transport visitors to far-off lands.<br><br>Epcot is also home to a variety of seasonal events and festivals that showcase the best of Disney magic and global culture. The Epcot International Flower & Garden Festival, held in the spring, features stunning displays of flowers and topiaries, as well as outdoor kitchens and live music performances. The Epcot International Food & Wine Festival, held in the fall, celebrates the culinary traditions of the world, with food and beverage booths, cooking demonstrations, and seminars by celebrity chefs.<br><br>To make the most of your visit to Epcot, it\'s important to plan ahead and consider factors such as park hours, crowd levels, and dining reservations. Be sure to check the park\'s schedule and plan your day accordingly, taking into account any shows or events that you don\'t want to miss. If you\'re planning to dine at one of Epcot\'s popular restaurants, such as Le Cellier Steakhouse or Teppan Edo, be sure to make a reservation in advance to avoid long wait times.<br><br>Whether you\'re a fan of technology, culture, or just good old-fashioned Disney fun, Epcot has something for everyone. So why not plan your next vacation around this iconic theme park and experience the magic of Walt Disney World like never before?', 'epcot/epcot1.jpg', 'Sorcerer Mickey Mouse made of shrubbery standing in front of Spaceship Earth.', 'epcot/epcot2.jpg', 'Hues of blue, purple, orange, red, pink and yellow reflect on Spaceship Earth in the nightlight.', 'epcot/epcot3.jpg', 'Front view of Main Cinema Street', 'epcot/epcot4.jpg', 'Princess Belle and The Beat made of shrubbery holding hands', '200 Epcot Center Dr, Lake Buena Vista, FL 32830', 'https://disneyworld.disney.go.com/destinations/epcot/', 'epcot/epcotmap.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/Epcot/@28.3752424,-81.5528624,17z/data=!4m10!1m2!2m1!1sepcot!3m6!1s0x88dd7fafde6c311b:0xea245263cb7597bd!8m2!3d28.3764687!4d-81.5494034!15sCgVlcGNvdFoHIgVlcGNvdJIBCnRoZW1lX3BhcmvgAQA!16zL20vMDliM2Y', 'Enjoy exciting attractions, themed festivals, international cuisine, live entertainment and more at EPCOT, a theme park at Walt Disney World Resort in Florida.', '109.00', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', ''),
(3, 'Disney\'s Animal Kingdom Theme Park', 'Disney\'s Animal Kingdom Theme Park is a world-renowned theme park that offers visitors a unique and immersive experience that combines the magic of Disney with the wonder of nature. Located in the heart of Walt Disney World Resort in Orlando, Florida, Animal Kingdom is a must-visit destination for animal lovers, thrill-seekers, and families alike.<br><br>Opened in 1998, Disney\'s Animal Kingdom Theme Park spans over 500 acres and is home to over 1,700 animals from over 250 species. The park is divided into several themed areas, including Africa, Asia, Discovery Island, Pandora – The World of Avatar, and DinoLand USA. Each area offers visitors the opportunity to explore and learn about different parts of the animal kingdom, as well as enjoy exciting rides, shows, and entertainment.<br><br>Animal Kingdom is home to a variety of thrilling rides and attractions that are sure to delight visitors of all ages. One of the park\'s most popular attractions is Kilimanjaro Safaris, a safari ride that takes visitors on a journey through the African savanna, where they can see elephants, lions, giraffes, and other majestic animals up close. Other popular attractions include Avatar Flight of Passage, an immersive 3D ride that allows visitors to fly on the back of a banshee, and Expedition Everest, a high-speed roller coaster that takes visitors on a journey through the Himalayan mountains.<br><br>In addition to rides, Animal Kingdom also offers a variety of shows and entertainment that are sure to delight visitors of all ages. Festival of the Lion King, a Broadway-style show that celebrates the music and culture of Africa, and Finding Nemo: The Musical, a live performance that brings the beloved Disney movie to life, are just a few of the shows that visitors can enjoy.<br><br>Animal Kingdom is not just a theme park, it is also a center for conservation and education. The park is home to several conservation programs that work to protect endangered species and their habitats, as well as educate visitors about the importance of wildlife conservation. Visitors can also participate in various educational programs and tours, such as the Wild Africa Trek, which takes visitors on a guided tour of the African savanna.<br><br>To make the most of your visit to Animal Kingdom, it\'s important to plan ahead and consider factors such as park hours, crowd levels, and dining reservations. Be sure to check the park\'s schedule and plan your day accordingly, taking into account any shows or events that you don\'t want to miss. If you\'re planning to dine at one of the park\'s many restaurants, be sure to make a reservation in advance to avoid long wait times. Additionally, be sure to dress appropriately for the weather and wear comfortable shoes, as Animal Kingdom is a large park with lots of walking involved.<br><br>In conclusion, Disney\'s Animal Kingdom Theme Park is a must-visit destination for anyone looking to experience the magic of Disney while also learning about and appreciating the natural world. With its thrilling rides, exciting shows, and commitment to conservation and education, Animal Kingdom is sure to provide a memorable experience for visitors of all ages.', 'animalkingdom/animalkingdom1.jpg', 'Forest and river view of \'The World of Avatar\' attraction', 'animalkingdom/animalkingdom2.jpg', 'Actor from Magic Kingdom \'The Lion King\' production pointing at the crowd', 'animalkingdom/animalkingdom3.jpg', 'Dinoland Attraction sign', 'animalkingdom/animalkingdom4.jpg', '\'The World of Avatar\' Pandora attraction', '2901 Osceola Pkwy, Lake Buena Vista, FL 32830', 'https://disneyworld.disney.go.com/destinations/animal-kingdom/', 'animalkingdom/animalkingdommap.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/search?q=animal%20kingdom&oq=animal+kingdom&aqs=chrome.0.0i271j46i131i433i512j46i20i131i175i199i263i433i512j0i131i433i512j0i20i263i433i512j69i60l3.2751j0j9&sourceid=chrome&ie=UTF-8&tbs=lf:1,lf_ui:1&tbm=lcl&sxsrf=AJOqlzUG5_DdoyP8Z1hT_FpcxpLM1-M26A:1677460956406&rflfq=1&num=10&rldimm=3762762187935006651&lqi=Cg5hbmltYWwga2luZ2RvbUjy9p8BWhgQABABGAAYASIOYW5pbWFsIGtpbmdkb22SAQp0aGVtZV9wYXJrmgEkQ2hkRFNVaE5NRzluUzBWSlEwRm5TVU56ZEUxVFVXZEJSUkFCqgEiEAEaHhABIhp9y2OjLCmLDRhhR9tfLZ_ESR_0UdLmZfA3ouABAA&phdesc=R3Uvbql2zyk&ved=2ahUKEwiQk7mDxbT9AhWNmmoFHR1JBMoQvS56BAgSEAE&sa=X&rlst=f#rlfi=hd:;si:3762762187935006651,l,Cg5hbmltYWwga2luZ2RvbUjy9p8BWhgQABABGAAYASIOYW5pbWFsIGtpbmdkb22SAQp0aGVtZV9wYXJrmgEkQ2hkRFNVaE5NRzluUzBWSlEwRm5TVU56ZEUxVFVXZEJSUkFCqgEiEAEaHhABIhp9y2OjLCmLDRhhR9tfLZ_ESR_0UdLmZfA3ouABAA,y,R3Uvbql2zyk;mv:[[28.366080099999998,-81.5871341],[28.3513737,-81.6069442]];tbs:lrf:!1m4!1u3!2m2!3m1!1e1!1m4!1u2!2m2!2m1!1e1!2m1!1e2!2m1!1e3!3sIAE,lf:1,lf_ui:1', 'Disney\'s Animal Kingdom Park is a Walt Disney World theme park with daily and nightly attractions and experiences, including Pandora – The World of Avatar.', '109.00', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', ''),
(4, 'Disney\'s Hollywood Studios', 'Disney\'s Hollywood Studios is a theme park that celebrates the magic of movies, television, and entertainment. Located in the heart of Walt Disney World Resort in Orlando, Florida, Hollywood Studios is a must-visit destination for movie lovers, thrill-seekers, and families alike.<>br<br>Opened in 1989, Disney\'s Hollywood Studios spans over 135 acres and is divided into several themed areas, including Hollywood Boulevard, Sunset Boulevard, Echo Lake, Toy Story Land, and Star Wars: Galaxy\'s Edge. Each area offers visitors the opportunity to explore and experience different aspects of the entertainment industry, as well as enjoy exciting rides, shows, and entertainment.<br><br>Hollywood Studios is home to a variety of thrilling rides and attractions that are sure to delight visitors of all ages. One of the park\'s most popular attractions is the Twilight Zone Tower of Terror, a high-speed drop ride that takes visitors on a spooky journey through the Hollywood Tower Hotel. Other popular attractions include Rock \'n\' Roller Coaster Starring Aerosmith, a thrilling roller coaster that takes visitors on a high-speed ride through the streets of Los Angeles, and Star Wars: Rise of the Resistance, an immersive ride that allows visitors to become part of the Star Wars universe.<br><br>In addition to rides, Hollywood Studios also offers a variety of shows and entertainment that are sure to delight visitors of all ages. Fantasmic!, a nighttime show that combines water, fire, and pyrotechnics with classic Disney characters, and Indiana Jones Epic Stunt Spectacular!, a live performance that brings the famous movie to life, are just a few of the shows that visitors can enjoy.<br><br>Hollywood Studios is home to a variety of dining options that offer visitors the chance to sample delicious food and drinks inspired by their favorite movies and television shows. From the sci-fi themed Docking Bay 7 Food and Cargo to the classic Hollywood Brown Derby restaurant, there\'s something for everyone at Hollywood Studios. Visitors can also browse the park\'s many shops, which offer a variety of souvenirs, gifts, and merchandise inspired by Disney and Hollywood.<br><br>To make the most of your visit to Hollywood Studios, it\'s important to plan ahead and consider factors such as park hours, crowd levels, and dining reservations. Be sure to check the park\'s schedule and plan your day accordingly, taking into account any shows or events that you don\'t want to miss. If you\'re planning to dine at one of the park\'s many restaurants, be sure to make a reservation in advance to avoid long wait times. Additionally, be sure to dress appropriately for the weather and wear comfortable shoes, as Hollywood Studios is a large park with lots of walking involved.<br><br>In conclusion, Disney\'s Hollywood Studios is a must-visit destination for anyone looking to experience the magic of movies and entertainment. With its thrilling rides, exciting shows, and commitment to providing an immersive experience for visitors, Hollywood Studios is sure to provide a memorable experience for visitors of all ages.\r\n', 'hollywoodstudios/hollywoodstudios1.jpg', 'Slink Dog Dash Roller Coaster', 'hollywoodstudios/hollywoodstudios2.jpg', 'The Simpson\'s Ride \'Krustyland\'', 'hollywoodstudios/hollywoodstudios3.jpg', 'View of the \'Hollywood Tower Hotel\'', 'hollywoodstudios/hollywoodstudios4.jpg', 'A scene from the \'Waterworld\' show', '351 S Studio Dr, Lake Buena Vista, FL 32830', 'https://disneyworld.disney.go.com/destinations/hollywood-studios/', 'hollywoodstudios/hollywoodstudiosmap.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/Disney\'s+Hollywood+Studios/@28.3580628,-81.5612862,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m6!3m5!1s0x88dd7c2763821e47:0xbbffcea336e3f10f!8m2!3d28.3580628!4d-81.5590975!16zL20vMDJtdjdn', 'Let your adventure begin at Disney\'s Hollywood Studios! Live shows, thrill attractions and fun for little ones. The Tower of Terror, Rock \'n\' Roller Coaster, Star Wars: Rise of the Resistance and more.', '109.00', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', ''),
(5, 'Universal Studios Florida', 'Universal Studios Florida is one of the world\'s most popular theme parks and an exciting destination for movie and TV fans. Located in Orlando, Florida, Universal Studios Florida offers visitors the opportunity to step into their favorite movies and television shows and experience thrilling rides, shows, and attractions.<br><br>\r\nOpened in 1990, Universal Studios Florida spans over 107 acres and is divided into several themed areas, including Hollywood, New York, San Francisco, and World Expo. Each area offers visitors a unique and immersive experience, with attractions, dining options, and entertainment inspired by iconic movies and television shows.<br><br>\r\nUniversal Studios Florida is home to a variety of exciting rides and attractions that are sure to delight visitors of all ages. Some of the park\'s most popular attractions include Harry Potter and the Escape from Gringotts, a thrilling ride that takes visitors on a journey through the wizarding world of Harry Potter, and The Simpsons Ride, a virtual reality ride that puts visitors in the middle of a wacky Simpsons adventure. Other popular attractions include Transformers: The Ride-3D, Revenge of the Mummy, and the Hollywood Rip Ride Rockit roller coaster.\r\n<br><br>\r\nIn addition to rides, Universal Studios Florida also offers a variety of shows and entertainment that are sure to delight visitors. From the high-energy spectacle of the Universal Orlando\'s Horror Make-Up Show to the entertaining and interactive character meet-and-greets, there\'s something for everyone at Universal Studios Florida.\r\n<br><br>\r\nUniversal Studios Florida is home to a variety of dining options that offer visitors the chance to sample delicious food and drinks inspired by their favorite movies and television shows. From the classic burgers and fries at Mel\'s Drive-In to the exotic flavors of the Wizarding World of Harry Potter, there\'s something for every taste bud. Visitors can also browse the park\'s many shops, which offer a variety of souvenirs, gifts, and merchandise inspired by Universal\'s iconic movies and television shows.\r\n<br><br>\r\nTo make the most of your visit to Universal Studios Florida, it\'s important to plan ahead and consider factors such as park hours, crowd levels, and dining reservations. Be sure to check the park\'s schedule and plan your day accordingly, taking into account any shows or events that you don\'t want to miss. If you\'re planning to dine at one of the park\'s many restaurants, be sure to make a reservation in advance to avoid long wait times. Additionally, be sure to dress appropriately for the weather and wear comfortable shoes, as Universal Studios Florida is a large park with lots of walking involved.\r\n<br><br>\r\nIn conclusion, Universal Studios Florida is a must-visit destination for anyone looking to experience the magic of movies and television shows. With its thrilling rides, exciting shows, and immersive experiences, Universal Studios Florida is sure to provide a memorable experience for visitors of all ages.', 'universalstudios/universal1.jpg', 'Universal Studios Globe', 'universalstudios/universal2.jpg', 'Mel\'s Drive In Diner', 'universalstudios/universal3.jpg', 'Kang and Kodos Statue from The Simpsons Ride', 'universalstudios/universal4.jpg', 'TRANSFORMERS: The Ride-3D', '6000 Universal Blvd, Orlando, FL 32819', 'https://www.universalorlando.com/web/en/us', 'universalstudios/universalmap.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/Universal+Studios+Florida/@28.4754282,-81.4698607,17z/data=!3m1!5s0x88e77ee77a719271:0xf362a4f577d8aa2f!4m6!3m5!1s0x88e77ec39415df75:0xf985d8fc7734a5a1!8m2!3d28.4754235!4d-81.467672!16zL20vMDVxc3lx', 'Take your vacation to the next level by exploring Universal Studios Orlando, Universal\'s Islands of Adventures, and Universal\'s Volcano Bay water park.', '109.00', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', ''),
(6, 'Universal\'s Island of Adventure', 'Universal\'s Islands of Adventure is a thrilling theme park located in Orlando, Florida that promises to take visitors on an unforgettable adventure through some of the world\'s most iconic stories and myths. With its immersive theming, thrilling rides, and exciting attractions, Islands of Adventure is a must-visit destination for any thrill seeker or theme park enthusiast.\r\n<br><br>\r\nOpened in 1999, Universal\'s Islands of Adventure spans over 101 acres and is divided into several themed areas, including Marvel Super Hero Island, Jurassic Park, The Wizarding World of Harry Potter, and more. Each area offers visitors a unique and immersive experience, with attractions, dining options, and entertainment inspired by popular movies and TV shows.\r\n<br><br>\r\nUniversal\'s Islands of Adventure is home to some of the world\'s most thrilling and innovative rides and attractions. One of the park\'s most popular attractions is The Wizarding World of Harry Potter, which includes two areas - Hogsmeade and Diagon Alley - and features rides such as Harry Potter and the Forbidden Journey and Hagrid\'s Magical Creatures Motorbike Adventure.\r\n<br><br>\r\nOther popular rides and attractions include The Amazing Adventures of Spider-Man, The Incredible Hulk Coaster, Skull Island: Reign of Kong, and Jurassic Park River Adventure. Visitors can also enjoy a variety of shows and entertainment, including The Eighth Voyage of Sinbad Stunt Show and The Poseidon\'s Fury Experience.\r\n<br><br>\r\nUniversal\'s Islands of Adventure is home to a variety of dining options that offer visitors the chance to sample delicious food and drinks inspired by their favorite movies and TV shows. From the hearty fare at Three Broomsticks in The Wizarding World of Harry Potter to the delicious burgers and fries at Captain America Diner, there\'s something for every taste bud. Visitors can also browse the park\'s many shops, which offer a variety of souvenirs, gifts, and merchandise inspired by the park\'s iconic stories and myths.\r\n<br><br>\r\nTo make the most of your visit to Universal\'s Islands of Adventure, it\'s important to plan ahead and consider factors such as park hours, crowd levels, and dining reservations. Be sure to check the park\'s schedule and plan your day accordingly, taking into account any shows or events that you don\'t want to miss. If you\'re planning to dine at one of the park\'s many restaurants, be sure to make a reservation in advance to avoid long wait times. Additionally, be sure to dress appropriately for the weather and wear comfortable shoes, as Universal\'s Islands of Adventure is a large park with lots of walking involved.\r\n<br><br>\r\nIn conclusion, Universal\'s Islands of Adventure is a thrilling and exciting theme park that promises to take visitors on a journey through some of the world\'s most iconic stories and myths. With its immersive theming, thrilling rides, and exciting attractions, Islands of Adventure is a must-visit destination for any theme park enthusiast.', 'islandofadventure/universal1.jpg', 'Universal Studios Globe', 'islandofadventure/island2.jpg', 'Hogwarts Express Train', 'islandofadventure/island3.jpg', 'Jurassic Park Entrance', 'islandofadventure/island4.jpg', 'The Amazing Adventures of Spider-Man', 'Universal Blvd, Orlando, FL 32819', 'https://www.universalorlando.com/web/en/us', 'islandofadventures/islandmap.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/Universal\'s+Islands+of+Adventure/@28.4718467,-81.4730768,17z/data=!4m6!3m5!1s0x88e77edfac4210bd:0x1364056e556d89f3!8m2!3d28.471842!4d-81.4708881!16zL20vMDVwcHE4', 'Take your vacation to the next level by exploring Universal Studios Orlando, Universal\'s Islands of Adventures, and Universal\'s Volcano Bay water park.', '109.00', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', ''),
(7, 'SeaWorld Orlando', 'SeaWorld Orlando is a marine-themed adventure park that combines exciting rides, immersive exhibits, and unforgettable animal encounters. Located in the heart of Orlando, Florida, SeaWorld offers visitors the chance to learn about and interact with some of the ocean\'s most fascinating creatures.\r\n<br><br>\r\nSeaWorld Orlando first opened its doors in 1973 and has since become one of the world\'s most popular marine adventure parks. With over 200 acres of rides, shows, and exhibits, SeaWorld offers visitors a variety of ways to experience marine life, from up-close encounters with dolphins and whales to thrilling roller coasters and water rides.\r\n<br><br>\r\nOne of SeaWorld\'s most popular attractions is the Shamu Show, where visitors can watch the park\'s resident killer whales perform acrobatic stunts and displays of strength and agility. The park is also home to a variety of other animal exhibits and shows, including Dolphin Days, where visitors can learn about and interact with bottlenose dolphins.\r\n<br><br>\r\nFor thrill-seekers, SeaWorld offers a variety of exciting rides and roller coasters, such as Mako, a hypercoaster that reaches speeds of up to 73 mph, and Infinity Falls, a thrilling water ride that takes visitors through rapids and waterfalls.\r\n<br><br>\r\nSeaWorld Orlando offers a variety of dining options for visitors, from quick service restaurants to full-service dining experiences. Visitors can enjoy everything from classic theme park fare like burgers and fries to more upscale options like sushi and seafood. The park also offers a variety of shopping options, including gift shops, specialty stores, and boutiques, where visitors can purchase souvenirs and merchandise inspired by the park\'s marine animals.\r\n<br><br>\r\nTo make the most of your visit to SeaWorld Orlando, it\'s important to plan ahead and consider factors such as park hours, crowd levels, and dining reservations. Be sure to check the park\'s schedule and plan your day accordingly, taking into account any shows or events that you don\'t want to miss. If you\'re planning to dine at one of the park\'s many restaurants, be sure to make a reservation in advance to avoid long wait times. Additionally, be sure to dress appropriately for the weather and wear comfortable shoes, as SeaWorld Orlando is a large park with lots of walking involved.\r\n<br><br>\r\nIn conclusion, SeaWorld Orlando is a unique and exciting marine-themed adventure park that offers visitors the chance to learn about and interact with some of the ocean\'s most fascinating creatures. With its immersive exhibits, thrilling rides, and unforgettable animal encounters, SeaWorld Orlando is a must-visit destination for any animal lover or theme park enthusiast.', 'seaworld/seaworld1.jpg', 'A whale jumping out of the water', 'seaworld/seaworld2.jpg', 'A turtle in the water', 'seaworld/seaworld3.jpg', 'Family watching sea creatures swim', 'seaworld/seaworld4.jpg', 'Dolphins swimming in the tank', '7007 Sea World Dr, Orlando, FL 32821', 'https://seaworld.com/orlando/?utm_source=google&utm_medium=organic&utm_campaign=gbp_listing', 'seaworld/seaworldmap.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/SeaWorld+Orlando/@28.409718,-81.4618994,17z/data=!4m6!3m5!1s0x88e77e288cd6237f:0x997f9e39a3d62bd5!8m2!3d28.409718!4d-81.4597107!16zL20vMGMyZGx5', 'Looking for amusement parks in Orlando? SeaWorld Orlando offers exciting rides and roller coasters, up-close animal encounters and more.', '99.99', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', ''),
(8, 'Legoland Florida', 'Legoland Florida is a theme park designed specifically for families with children ages 2-12. Located in Winter Haven, Florida, Legoland offers a variety of rides, attractions, and shows that combine the fun of building with Lego bricks with the excitement of a theme park.\r\n<br><br>\r\nLegoland Florida first opened in 2011 and has since become a popular destination for families visiting the Orlando area. The park is divided into several themed areas, each with its own unique rides, attractions, and dining options.\r\n<br><br>\r\nOne of the park\'s most popular attractions is Miniland USA, where visitors can explore a miniature version of some of America\'s most famous landmarks and cities, all built entirely out of Lego bricks. Other popular attractions include the Lego Ninjago Ride, where riders can use hand gestures to battle villains and earn points, and the Duplo Farm, where younger children can enjoy a variety of interactive play experiences.\r\n<br><br>\r\nFor thrill-seekers, Legoland Florida offers several roller coasters and water rides, such as the Dragon Coaster and the Quest for Chi water ride. There are also several live shows and character meet-and-greets, such as the Lego Friends to entertain visitors.\r\n<br><br>\r\nLegoland Florida offers a variety of dining options for visitors, from quick service restaurants to sit-down dining experiences. Visitors can enjoy everything from classic theme park fare like hot dogs and pizza to healthier options like salads and sandwiches. The park also offers a variety of shopping options, including gift shops, specialty stores, and boutiques, where visitors can purchase Lego sets and other merchandise inspired by the park\'s themes.\r\n<br><br>\r\nTo make the most of your visit to Legoland Florida, it\'s important to plan ahead and consider factors such as park hours, crowd levels, and dining reservations. Be sure to check the park\'s schedule and plan your day accordingly, taking into account any shows or events that you don\'t want to miss. If you\'re planning to dine at one of the park\'s many restaurants, be sure to make a reservation in advance to avoid long wait times. Additionally, be sure to dress appropriately for the weather and wear comfortable shoes, as Legoland Florida is a large park with lots of walking involved.\r\n<br><br>\r\nIn conclusion, Legoland Florida is a unique and exciting theme park that offers families with young children the chance to experience the world of Lego in a fun and interactive way. With its immersive themed areas, exciting rides, and family-friendly atmosphere, Legoland Florida is a must-visit destination for any Lego fan or theme park enthusiast.', 'legoland/legoland1.jpg', 'Lego boats floating in the water', 'legoland/legoland2.jpg', 'Lego Yoda', '', 'Lego Pirates playing instruments', 'legoland/legoland4.jpg', 'Fun Town Entrance Sign', 'One LEGOLAND Way Winter Haven, FL 33884', 'https://www.legoland.com/florida/', 'legoland/legolandmap.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/LEGOLAND%C2%AE+Florida+Resort/@27.9897179,-81.6903413,18z/data=!4m6!3m5!1s0x88dd0d887ee5cadf:0xbc6c5dcfe838271a!8m2!3d27.9885659!4d-81.6910418!16s%2Fm%2F0b6d60t', 'Plan your next LEGOLAND® Florida visit and build memories that last a lifetime, featuring 2 theme parks, a water park, and 3 fully themed Resort hotels.', '84.00', '', 0, 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', ''),
(9, 'Gatorland', 'Gatorland is the \"Alligator Capital of the World!\" This unique destination offers a thrilling and educational experience for visitors of all ages.\r\n<br><br>\r\nAs one of Central Florida\'s oldest attractions, Gatorland has been wowing guests for over 70 years with its impressive collection of alligators, crocodiles, and other exotic animals. The park spans over 110 acres and features various habitats, exhibits, and shows that showcase the fascinating world of these prehistoric creatures.\r\n<br><br>\r\nOne of the park\'s highlights is the Gator Jumparoo Show, where you can witness giant alligators jumping high out of the water to snatch their prey. You can also explore the \"Screamin\' Gator Zip Line\" and soar over the park\'s alligator breeding marsh. This exhilarating experience is not for the faint of heart but is sure to leave you with unforgettable memories.\r\n<br><br>\r\nIf you\'re interested in learning more about alligators and their habitat, make sure to take a stroll along the boardwalk through the breeding marsh. Here, you\'ll have a chance to observe the alligators in their natural habitat and learn about their behaviors and mating rituals.\r\n<br><br>\r\nGatorland also features a variety of other animal exhibits, including a petting zoo, bird sanctuary, and swamp walk. The park\'s newest addition is \"Stompin\' Gator Off-Road Adventure,\" where you can take a wild ride on a customized off-road vehicle and get up close to the park\'s gators, as well as other animals like wild boar, zebra, and more.\r\n<br><br>\r\nFor those looking for a more personal experience, Gatorland offers a \"Trainer for a Day\" program where you can work side-by-side with the park\'s trainers and learn about the daily care of the animals.\r\n<br><br>\r\nGatorland is also committed to conservation efforts and offers various educational programs to teach visitors about the importance of protecting these incredible creatures.\r\n<br><br>\r\nOverall, Gatorland is a must-visit destination for anyone looking to experience the wild side of Florida and get up close to some of the most fascinating creatures on the planet.', 'gatorland/gatorland1.jpg', 'Two gators laying in the lake', 'gatorland/gatorland2.jpg', 'A bright red, greed, and blue colored Macaw Bird', 'gatorland/gatorland3.jpg', 'Two flamingos in the water', 'gatorland/gatorland4.jpg', 'Two Macaw Birds sitting on branches', '14501 S Orange Blossom Trl, Orlando, FL 32837', 'https://www.gatorland.com/', 'gatorland/gatorlandmap.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/Gatorland/@28.3560699,-81.4067957,18z/data=!4m6!3m5!1s0x88dd871e1bd911f5:0xf334076b2158659d!8m2!3d28.3559542!4d-81.4040247!16zL20vMDhmd3py', 'The self-proclaimed \'Alligator Capital of The World\', <b class=\"actInfo\">Gatorland</b> is home to hundreds of Florida\'s original residents.', '32.99', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, '', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', ''),
(10, 'Sea Life Orlando Aquarium', 'SEA LIFE Orlando Aquarium is a perfect place to explore the mysteries of the underwater world. Located in the heart of Orlando, this attraction is perfect for all ages and provides an unforgettable experience.\r\n<br><br>\r\nSEA LIFE Orlando Aquarium features over 5,000 sea creatures in a unique and interactive environment. The aquarium has various zones, each showcasing different marine ecosystems such as the Indian Ocean, Pacific Ocean, and the Caribbean. The popular 360-degree ocean tunnel allows visitors to walk through the tunnel while enjoying the breathtaking view of sea creatures swimming above and around them.\r\n<br><br>\r\nThe aquarium also features interactive exhibits that allow visitors to get up close and personal with marine life. The interactive touch pool offers an opportunity to touch starfish and other creatures while learning about their habitats and behaviors. The Jellyfish Wall exhibit is another must-see experience that offers a mesmerizing view of jellyfish in their unique habitats.\r\n<br><br>\r\nSEA LIFE Orlando Aquarium offers many educational programs, including guided tours and interactive presentations. These programs are perfect for groups, families, and students who want to learn about the marine world and its inhabitants. SEA LIFE Orlando Aquarium also has a dedicated conservation team that works to protect and preserve marine life.\r\n<br><br>\r\nThe aquarium also offers unique experiences like shark diving and snorkeling with rays. The shark diving experience is perfect for thrill-seekers, while the snorkeling experience provides a unique opportunity to get up close with rays and other marine life.\r\n<br><br>\r\nSEA LIFE Orlando Aquarium is conveniently located on International Drive and is easily accessible from all major theme parks and hotels. The aquarium is open seven days a week, and tickets can be purchased online or at the gate.\r\n<br><br>\r\nOverall, SEA LIFE Orlando Aquarium is a must-visit destination for anyone who loves marine life and wants to experience the underwater world up close. With its unique exhibits, interactive displays, and educational programs, it\'s the perfect place for families, groups, and individuals to have a fun and educational experience.', 'sealife/sealife1.jpg', '', 'sealife/sealife2.jpg', '', 'sealife/sealife3.jpg', '', 'sealife/sealife4.jpg', '', '8449 International Dr, Orlando, FL 32819', 'https://www.visitsealife.com/orlando/', 'sealife/sealifemap.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/8449+International+Dr,+Orlando,+FL+32819/@28.4425892,-81.4707755,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m6!3m5!1s0x88e77e52513ab709:0xc8defea5b2c89f9d!8m2!3d28.4425845!4d-81.4685868!16s%2Fg%2F11cs6kjzf6', 'Explore the depths of the ocean at Sea Life Orlando Aquarium and experience the wonders of marine life with thrilling rides, amazing attractions, and unforgettable encounters!', '34.99', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', ''),
(11, 'Hard Rock Cafe', 'Hard Rock Cafe is the ultimate rock \'n\' roll dining experience! Located in the heart of Orlando, our restaurant is a must-visit destination for music lovers and foodies alike.\r\n<br><br>\r\nAs soon as you enter our restaurant, you\'ll be surrounded by music memorabilia from some of the biggest names in rock history. From guitars and drum sets to autographed photos and clothing worn by iconic musicians, you\'ll be immersed in the world of rock \'n\' roll.\r\n<br><br>\r\nOur menu is just as impressive as our collection of memorabilia. Start off with our famous Jumbo Combo appetizer, featuring an assortment of our most popular starters. Then, try one of our delicious burgers, made with fresh, never frozen beef, or choose from one of our signature entrees like our Hickory Smoked Ribs or Grilled Norwegian Salmon.\r\n<br><br>\r\nDon\'t forget to save room for dessert! Our desserts are just as legendary as our rock \'n\' roll memorabilia, with options like our Classic New York Cheesecake or our famous Hot Fudge Brownie.\r\n<br><br>\r\nAnd of course, no visit to the Hard Rock Cafe would be complete without checking out our Rock Shop, where you can take home your own piece of rock \'n\' roll history. From t-shirts and hoodies to collectible pins and shot glasses, you\'ll find the perfect souvenir to remember your visit.\r\n<br><br>\r\nWhether you\'re a die-hard music fan or just looking for a unique dining experience, the Hard Rock Cafe Orlando is the perfect destination. Join us for lunch or dinner, and let us rock your taste buds!', 'hardrock/hardrock1.jpg', '', 'hardrock/hardrock2.jpg', '', 'hardrock/hardrock3.jpg', '', 'hardrock/hardrock4.jpg', '', '6050 Universal Blvd, Orlando, FL 32819', 'https://www.hardrockcafe.com/location/orlando/', 'hardrock/hardrockmap.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/6050+Universal+Blvd,+Orlando,+FL+32819/@28.4737976,-81.4697375,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m6!3m5!1s0x88e77ee0bfb69dcf:0xacdabf5ba0f2909f!8m2!3d28.4737929!4d-81.4675488!16s%2Fg%2F11b8v500kw', 'Experience the ultimate music-lovers paradise at Hard Rock Cafe and explore a world of delicious food, amazing cocktails, and unforgettable memories!', '$$', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', ''),
(12, 'Aquatica Orlando', 'Aquatica Orlando is a water park where the thrills and relaxation of the beach come together in one unforgettable experience! Located in the heart of Orlando, this park features a variety of water attractions for all ages.\r\n<br><br>\r\nGet ready to take on some of the most thrilling water rides, such as Ihu\'s Breakaway Falls, where you\'ll experience a heart-pumping free fall, or Ray Rush, where you\'ll twist and turn through a water adventure. If you\'re looking for something more relaxing, you can float down Loggerhead Lane, a lazy river that takes you through an underwater world filled with exotic fish and beautiful scenery.\r\n<br><br>\r\nAquatica Orlando is also home to some of the most amazing marine animals, including Commerson\'s dolphins, who perform in the Dolphin Plunge attraction. You can also interact with playful and friendly stingrays in the Ray Encounter attraction or take part in the unique experience of hand-feeding exotic birds at Roa\'s Aviary.\r\n<br><br>\r\nFor younger guests, there\'s a dedicated children\'s area called Kata\'s Kookaburra Cove, with smaller versions of the park\'s water slides and interactive water features. Parents can relax and enjoy the sun on the lounge chairs located in the nearby shade.\r\n<br><br>\r\nIn addition to the water attractions, Aquatica Orlando also offers dining and shopping experiences, with a variety of options for every taste and budget. From delicious burgers and fries to fresh salads and smoothies, there\'s something for everyone.\r\n<br><br>\r\nTo make the most of your visit, be sure to check out the park\'s daily schedule for shows, concerts, and special events. You won\'t want to miss the chance to catch one of the many live performances that take place throughout the day.\r\n<br><br>\r\nOverall, Aquatica Orlando offers a unique and exciting water adventure for the whole family, with something for everyone to enjoy. So come make a splash and create unforgettable memories at one of Orlando\'s premier water parks.', 'aquatica/aquatica1.jpg', '', 'aquatica/aquatica2.jpg', '', 'aquatica/aquatica3.jpg', '', 'aquatica/aquatica4.jpg', '', '5800 Water Play Way, Orlando, FL 32821', 'https://aquatica.com/orlando/', 'aquatica/aquaticamap.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/Aquatica+Orlando/@28.4158689,-81.4584786,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m6!3m5!1s0x88e77e24bf3d1e71:0x669ac848350fb511!8m2!3d28.4158642!4d-81.4562899!16s%2Fm%2F011cgl9q', 'Explore the aquatic world of Aquatica Orlando and experience an unforgettable adventure full of thrilling rides, amazing attractions, and unique marine life!', '47.99', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'Y', ''),
(13, 'Fun Spot America Theme Parks', 'If you\'re looking for family-friendly fun in Orlando, look no further than Fun Spot America Theme Parks. With two locations in the area, you can enjoy a variety of thrilling rides and attractions, as well as games and food options.\r\n<br><br>\r\nAt Fun Spot America, there\'s something for everyone. For the adrenaline seekers, check out the park\'s signature rides like the White Lightning wooden coaster, the Mine Blower steel coaster, or the SkyCoaster. If you\'re looking for something tamer, there are plenty of other options like the Ferris wheel, bumper cars, and go-karts.\r\n<br><br>\r\nOne of the best things about Fun Spot America is its affordability. Unlike some of the bigger theme parks in the area, you don\'t have to break the bank to have a great time here. Admission is free, and you can purchase tickets for individual rides or an unlimited ride wristband at a reasonable price. Plus, parking is always free.\r\n<br><br>\r\nIn addition to the rides and attractions, Fun Spot America also features a variety of midway games where you can win prizes, as well as a selection of food and drink options. Whether you\'re craving a funnel cake or a burger and fries, there\'s something to satisfy your hunger.\r\n<br><br>\r\nIf you\'re looking for a unique experience, check out the park\'s virtual reality attraction, where you can step into a whole new world and experience the thrill of a roller coaster in a completely different way.\r\n<br><br>\r\nOverall, Fun Spot America Theme Parks are a great choice for a day of family fun. With two convenient locations in Orlando, it\'s easy to plan a visit and enjoy all that the parks have to offer. From thrilling rides to midway games and food options, there\'s something for everyone here. And with affordable prices, you can have a great time without breaking the bank.', 'funspot/funspot1.jpg', '', 'funspot/funspot2.jpg', '', 'funspot/funspot3.jpg', '', 'funspot/funspot4.jpg', '', '5700 Fun Spot Way, Orlando, FL 32819', 'https://fun-spot.com/', 'funspot/funspotmap.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/Fun+Spot+America+Theme+Parks/@28.4654223,-81.457746,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m6!3m5!1s0x88e77eede1867879:0x3a8bdd16562ed7bd!8m2!3d28.4654176!4d-81.4555573!16s%2Fg%2F12lvpwh3j', 'Experience the ultimate fun and adventure at Fun Spot America Theme Parks and explore a world of thrilling rides, amazing attractions, and unforgettable memories!', '59.95', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'Y', ''),
(14, 'Bubba Gump Shrimp Co.', 'Bubba Gump Shrimp Co. is a restaurant that takes you on a journey inspired by the film \"Forrest Gump.\" With several locations worldwide, including Orlando, Bubba Gump is a must-visit restaurant for those seeking delicious seafood, a fun atmosphere, and movie nostalgia.\r\n<br><br>\r\nThe Orlando location of Bubba Gump Shrimp Co. is conveniently located at the entrance of Universal CityWalk. This themed restaurant provides a casual and comfortable atmosphere that captures the essence of the classic movie. The restaurant features various memorabilia from the film, including a replica of the iconic shrimp boat \"Jenny.\"\r\n<br><br>\r\nAt Bubba Gump Shrimp Co., the menu showcases fresh seafood dishes, including shrimp, crab, lobster, and fish. Their famous coconut shrimp is a must-try, as is their delicious seafood gumbo. They also offer non-seafood options, such as burgers and salads, ensuring there is something for everyone. For those over 21, they offer a selection of signature drinks, including the famous \"Lt. Dan\'s Pomegranate Punch.\"\r\n<br><br>\r\nIn addition to the delicious food and drinks, the restaurant offers unique entertainment for guests. They have a trivia game that tests your knowledge of the movie, and if you answer correctly, you\'ll receive a free dessert. The restaurant also provides an outdoor seating area that overlooks the beautiful Universal CityWalk, allowing guests to enjoy the view while dining.\r\n<br><br>\r\nBubba Gump Shrimp Co. is also an ideal location for group events and celebrations, including birthdays, corporate events, and even weddings. The restaurant offers special event packages that cater to your specific needs, including personalized menus and decor.\r\n<br><br>\r\nOverall, Bubba Gump Shrimp Co. provides a memorable dining experience with fantastic food, excellent service, and fun entertainment. Whether you\'re visiting Orlando or a local, make sure to add this restaurant to your itinerary for a delightful meal and a touch of movie nostalgia.', 'bubba/bubba1.jpg', '', 'bubba/bubba2.jpg', '', 'bubba/bubba3.jpg', '', 'bubba/bubba4.jpg', '', '6000 Universal Blvd Suite 735, Orlando, FL 32819', 'https://www.bubbagump.com/location/bubba-gump-orlando-fl/', 'bubba/bubbamap.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/Bubba+Gump+Shrimp+Co./@28.4731566,-81.467021,17z/data=!3m2!4b1!5s0x88e77ee7321cddc7:0x4c44305acd60cb1d!4m6!3m5!1s0x88e77ee72bc69fc1:0x3a2014bf7654132c!8m2!3d28.4731519!4d-81.4648323!16s%2Fg%2F1th296vh', 'Enjoy a delicious meal of fresh seafood and delectable flavors at Bubba Gump Shrimp Co. and explore a world of mouth-watering dishes, amazing cocktails, and unforgettable memories!', '$$', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', '');
