(15, 'The Cowfish Sushi Burger Bar', 'The Cowfish Sushi Burger Bar is a unique restaurant located in the heart of Orlando, Florida. This popular eatery offers guests the opportunity to indulge in a truly one-of-a-kind dining experience. With a creative menu that blends the best of both worlds - sushi and burgers - The Cowfish Sushi Burger Bar is a must-visit destination for foodies and families alike.\r\n<br><br>\r\nThe menu at The Cowfish Sushi Burger Bar is diverse, featuring a variety of sushi rolls, burgers, and signature dishes that will tantalize your taste buds. Highlights include the Fusion Specialty Sushi Rolls like the \"All-American Bacon Double Cheeseburgooshi\" - a sushi roll that combines the flavors of an American cheeseburger with the presentation of sushi. For the burger-lovers, the \"Burgushi\'\' options like the \"The Cowfish Has Officially Left The Building\" is a must-try, with its combination of beef, bacon, cheese, and avocado rolled in soy paper and served with a side of garlic aioli.\r\n<br><br>\r\nThe Cowfish Sushi Burger Bar offers more than just delicious food, as the restaurant\'s decor is a feast for the eyes as well. The dining area is decorated in a modern, industrial style, complete with exposed brick walls, steel beams, and unique lighting fixtures. Guests can also dine outside on the patio, which offers a beautiful view of the surrounding area.\r\n<br><br>\r\nIn addition to the dining experience, The Cowfish Sushi Burger Bar offers a full bar, including an extensive list of signature cocktails, beers, and wines. Happy hour specials are available daily, making it the perfect spot to unwind after a long day of exploring Orlando.\r\n<br><br>\r\nOverall, The Cowfish Sushi Burger Bar is a must-visit restaurant in Orlando. With its creative menu, beautiful decor, and lively atmosphere, this eatery has something for everyone.', 'cowfish/cowfish1.jpg', '', 'cowfish/cowfish2.jpg', '', 'cowfish/cowfish3.jpg', '', 'cowfish/cowfish4.jpg', '', '6000 Universal Blvd, Orlando, FL 32819', 'https://www.universalorlando.com/web/en/us/things-to-do/dining/the-cowfish', 'cowfish/cowfishmap.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/The+Cowfish®+Sushi+Burger+Bar/@28.4730103,-81.4676568,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m6!3m5!1s0x88e77ee73de1f549:0x2777135cc55bf9e5!8m2!3d28.4730056!4d-81.4654681!16s%2Fg%2F11b6lmwq9v', 'Indulge in a unique culinary experience at The Cowfish Sushi Burger Bar and explore a world of creative cuisine, amazing cocktails, and unforgettable memories!', '$$', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', ''),
(16, 'The Cheesecake Factory', 'The Cheesecake Factory is a popular restaurant chain that has been serving up American cuisine and delicious cheesecakes since its founding in Beverly Hills in 1978. The I-Drive location is a popular destination for both locals and tourists, and its elegant and upscale atmosphere makes it a great spot for any occasion.\r\n<br><br>\r\nThe restaurant\'s menu is extensive, with options to please any palate. Guests can start with classic appetizers like buffalo wings or opt for unique dishes like the avocado egg rolls. Main courses range from salads and sandwiches to pasta dishes and seafood entrees. Of course, no visit to The Cheesecake Factory is complete without trying one of their famous cheesecakes, which come in a variety of flavors and are baked fresh daily. The restaurant is known for its generous portion sizes, so guests are advised to come hungry and be prepared to take home leftovers.\r\n<br><br>\r\nIn addition to its impressive food menu, The Cheesecake Factory also offers an extensive drink menu, including specialty cocktails, beer, and wine. The restaurant\'s commitment to quality extends to its drink offerings, with many options featuring high-end spirits and fresh ingredients.\r\n<br><br>\r\nOne interesting fact about The Cheesecake Factory is that its founder, David Overton, originally planned to open a bakery. However, after spending time in Europe and seeing the popularity of restaurants that combined both bakery and restaurant concepts, he decided to open a full-service restaurant that would feature his mother\'s recipe for cheesecake. The rest, as they say, is history.\r\n<br><br>\r\nOverall, The Cheesecake Factory is a beloved restaurant chain that offers a unique dining experience on I-Drive. With its extensive menu, impressive drink selection, and famous cheesecakes, it provides a great option for casual and upscale dining alike.', 'cheesecake/cheesecake1.jpg', '', 'cheesecake/cheesecake2.jpg', '', 'cheesecake/cheesecake3.jpg', '', 'cheesecake/cheesecake4.jpg', '', '4200 Conroy Rd, Orlando, FL 32839', 'https://locations.thecheesecakefactory.com/fl/orlando-56.html', 'cheesecake/cheesecakemap.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/The+Cheesecake+Factory/@28.4855416,-81.4336935,17z/data=!3m1!5s0x88e77ea89277535b:0xc7538d03a61aab98!4m15!1m8!3m7!1s0x88e77ea89603bd9d:0x4247117802c9d416!2s4200+Conroy+Rd,+Orlando,+FL+32839!3b1!8m2!3d28.4855369!4d-81.4315048!16s%2Fg%2F11c5q0zvlp!3m5!1s0x88e77ea893b83cbf:0x8c5b51fd6bb065be!8m2!3d28.4860031!4d-81.4313344!16s%2Fg%2F1vzn6cyn', 'Indulge in an unforgettable dining experience at The Cheesecake Factory and explore a world of delicious dishes, amazing cocktails, and unforgettable memories!', '$$', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', ''),
(17, 'Paddlefish', 'Nestled in the heart of Orlando\'s bustling International Drive, Paddlefish is a seafood restaurant with a difference. Set aboard a beautifully restored 1920s riverboat, Paddlefish offers a unique and unforgettable dining experience. As you step on board, you\'ll be greeted by an elegant and sophisticated atmosphere that is both modern and classic in its design.\r\n<br><br>\r\nSeafood lovers will be spoilt for choice at Paddlefish, with an extensive menu featuring everything from classic starters like oysters and shrimp cocktail to more unique dishes like lobster corn dogs and crab cakes. The main course offerings are equally impressive, with options ranging from whole fish and seafood towers to pasta dishes and steak. Paddlefish also boasts a raw bar where guests can select from a range of fresh oysters, clams and other seafood options.\r\n<br><br>\r\nAs you browse the menu, be sure to take a look at the restaurant\'s drink offerings. Paddlefish has a reputation for its extensive drink menu, which includes specialty cocktails, wines and beer. The cocktail menu is particularly noteworthy, with options featuring high-end spirits and fresh ingredients. The wine list is equally impressive, with a range of domestic and international options available to pair perfectly with your meal.\r\n<br><br>\r\nThe boat that the restaurant is housed on, the Empress Lily, was originally owned by Walt Disney World and was used as a floating restaurant from the late 1970s until 1995. After being retired and sitting unused for several years, the boat was purchased and restored to its former glory. Today, it provides the perfect setting for a unique and memorable dining experience on I-Drive.', 'paddlefish/paddlefish1.jpg', '', 'paddlefish/paddlefish2.jpg', '', 'paddlefish/paddlefish3.jpg', '', '', '', '1670 Buena Vista Dr, Orlando, FL 32830', 'https://www.paddlefishrestaurant.com/', 'paddlefish/paddlefishmap.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/Paddlefish/@28.3718997,-81.5191227,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m6!3m5!1s0x88dd7f8658ede64b:0xcdb55d5724da224b!8m2!3d28.371895!4d-81.516934!16s%2Fg%2F1tsjfg1d', 'Experience the ultimate seafood adventure at <b class=\"actInfo\">Paddlefish</b> and explore a world of delicious dishes, amazing cocktails, and unforgettable memories!', '$$$', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', ''),
(18, 'The Melting Pot', 'The Melting Pot, located in Orlando\'s International Drive, is a restaurant that offers a unique and interactive dining experience that is perfect for couples, families, and groups of friends. As you step inside, you\'ll be struck by the warm and inviting atmosphere, complete with intimate lighting and comfortable seating.\r\n<br><br>\r\nOne of the most unique features of The Melting Pot is the fondue pot that sits at the center of each table. The restaurant\'s fondue options include cheese, broth, and chocolate, and guests can select from a variety of meats, vegetables, and breads to dip into the pot and cook to their liking. The interactive nature of the fondue experience makes it perfect for groups to enjoy together, or for couples looking for a romantic night out.\r\n<br><br>\r\nIn addition to the fondue, The Melting Pot offers a range of delicious appetizers, entrees, and desserts. The restaurant\'s menu includes a variety of gourmet salads, seafood and meat dishes, and a range of chocolate fondue options for dessert. The Melting Pot also offers an extensive wine and cocktail list to complement your meal and enhance your dining experience.\r\n<br><br>\r\nThe Melting Pot has an interesting history. The restaurant was first established in 1975 in Maitland, Florida, and has since expanded to locations throughout the United States and internationally. The concept for the restaurant was developed by a group of friends who were inspired by the idea of creating a unique and interactive dining experience that would bring people together. Today, The Melting Pot continues to be a beloved dining destination for those looking for a fun and memorable night out on I-Drive.', 'melt/melt1.jpg', '', 'melt/melt2.jpg', '', 'melt/melt3.jpg', '', 'melt/melt4.jpg', '', '7549 W Sand Lake Rd, Orlando, FL 32819', 'https://www.meltingpot.com/orlando-fl/', 'melt/meltmap.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/The+Melting+Pot/@28.5703644,-81.5085198,12z/data=!4m10!1m2!2m1!1smelting+pot!3m6!1s0x88e77fa654b7e4a7:0x48a2b1fe2455c27e!8m2!3d28.4507542!4d-81.4855943!15sCgttZWx0aW5nIHBvdCIDiAEBWg0iC21lbHRpbmcgcG90kgERZm9uZHVlX3Jlc3RhdXJhbnTgAQA!16s%2Fg%2F1tzgq0vf', 'Enjoy an unforgettable fondue experience at The Melting Pot and explore a world of delicious dishes, amazing cocktails, and unforgettable memories!', '$$$', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', ''),
(19, 'The Capital Grille', 'Being among the top restaurants and attractions of Orlando\'s vibrant International Drive, Capital Grille is an elegant and sophisticated steakhouse that provides an unparalleled dining experience. As you enter the restaurant, you\'ll be welcomed by the grand and stylish decor, with a mix of modern and classic elements that exude luxury.\r\n<br><br>\r\nOne of the highlights of Capital Grille is the extensive wine list, which features over 350 carefully curated selections from around the world. Whether you\'re a wine connoisseur or just looking to enjoy a glass with your meal, the knowledgeable staff is on hand to help you select the perfect pairing to enhance your dining experience.\r\n<br><br>\r\nIn addition to the wine, Capital Grille offers a range of expertly prepared steaks, seafood, and other classic American dishes. The restaurant\'s menu includes signature cuts like the dry-aged Porterhouse and the bone-in ribeye, as well as seasonal specials and a variety of sides and desserts.\r\n<br><br>\r\nCapital Grille was founded in 1990 in Providence, Rhode Island. Today, the restaurant has locations across the United States, and has become known for its commitment to exceptional quality and service. Whether you\'re celebrating a special occasion or just looking for a memorable night out, Capital Grille is the perfect destination for a fine dining experience on International Drive.', 'capgrille/capgrille1.jpg', '', 'capgrille/capgrille2.jpg', '', 'capgrille/capgrille3.jpg', '', 'capgrille/capgrille4.jpg', '', '9101 International Dr Suite 1000, Orlando, FL 32819', 'https://www.thecapitalgrille.com/locations/fl/orlando/orlando-i-drive/8025', 'capgrille/capgrillemap.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/The+Capital+Grille/@28.4308409,-81.4723843,17z/data=!3m2!4b1!5s0x88e77e4b1da3fa15:0x7edf0a3a7257fc65!4m6!3m5!1s0x88e77e4ade2aa501:0x3a2b2c88d2acb985!8m2!3d28.4308362!4d-81.4701956!16s%2Fg%2F1tp282mr', 'Enjoy an exquisite dining experience at The Capital Grille and explore a world of delicious dishes, amazing cocktails, and unforgettable memories!', '$$$$', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', ''),
(20, 'Fogo de Chão Brazilian Steakhouse', 'Indulge in an authentic Brazilian dining experience at Fogo de Chao, located on the bustling International Drive in Orlando. From the moment you step inside, you\'ll be transported to a world of warmth and hospitality, with a warm and inviting atmosphere that makes you feel right at home.\r\n<br><br>\r\nAt Fogo de Chao, the star of the show is the churrasco-style dining, where a parade of expertly prepared meats are carved tableside by the skilled gauchos. From juicy and flavorful sirloin to tender lamb chops and succulent pork ribs, every bite is an explosion of flavor that will leave your taste buds dancing.\r\n<br><br>\r\nIn addition to the meats, Fogo de Chao also offers a selection of fresh salads, charcuterie, and hot sides to round out your dining experience. And be sure to save room for the dessert, which includes delectable options like the chocolate mousse cake and the papaya cream.\r\n<br><br>\r\nFogo de Chao has a rich history that dates back to the early 19th century in the southern region of Brazil. The restaurant\'s name means \"fire of the ground,\" which refers to the traditional cooking technique of slow-roasting meats over an open flame. Today, Fogo de Chao has locations across the United States, and has become known for its commitment to quality and exceptional service.\r\n<br><br>\r\nWhether you\'re celebrating a special occasion or just looking for a memorable dining experience, Fogo de Chao on International Drive is the perfect destination for an unforgettable taste of Brazil.', 'fogo/fogo1.jpg', '', 'fogo/fogo2.jpg', '', 'fogo/fogo3.jpg', '', 'fogo/fogo4.jpg', '', '8282 International Dr, Orlando, FL 32819', 'https://fogodechao.com/location/orlando/', 'fogo/fogomap.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/Fogo+de+Chão+Brazilian+Steakhouse/@28.4458479,-81.4738958,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m6!3m5!1s0x88e77e5350a0d697:0xf2135e27aa52033!8m2!3d28.4458432!4d-81.4717071!16s%2Fg%2F1hc4ljw52', 'Fogo de Chão Brazilian Steakhouse is a premier dining experience that offers a unique blend of authentic Southern Brazilian cuisine, with a variety of high-quality, simply prepared meats fire-roasted to perfection.', '$$$', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', ''),
(21, 'ICEBAR Orlando', 'Experience the ultimate frozen adventure at ICEBAR Orlando, a unique and unforgettable attraction located on International Drive in the heart of Orlando. Step into a winter wonderland and prepare to be amazed by the stunning ice sculptures, vibrant colors, and unique atmosphere that will transport you to a world of frozen fantasy.\r\n<br><br>\r\nUpon entering ICEBAR Orlando, you\'ll be greeted by a friendly host who will guide you through the experience. Don\'t worry about the cold, as you\'ll be provided with a cozy thermal cape and gloves to keep you warm throughout your visit. As you explore the ice bar, you\'ll be amazed by the intricate ice sculptures, carved by expert artists who use chainsaws and chisels to create stunning masterpieces.\r\n<br><br>\r\nOne of the highlights of ICEBAR Orlando is the impressive drink menu, which features an array of delicious cocktails and frozen drinks that are served in glasses made entirely of ice. From classics like the margarita to more unique options like the Iceberg, there\'s something for every taste.\r\n<br><br>\r\nIn addition to the ice bar, ICEBAR Orlando also features a Fire Lounge, where you can warm up with a cozy fireplace and comfortable seating. And be sure to check out the Chill Lounge, which features a unique igloo-style design and is perfect for relaxing with friends.\r\n<br><br>\r\nICEBAR Orlando has a fascinating history, having been founded in 2007 as the first permanent ice bar in the United States. Today, it continues to be a must-visit destination for locals and tourists alike, providing a one-of-a-kind experience that you won\'t find anywhere else.\r\n<br><br>\r\nWhether you\'re looking for a unique date night, a fun outing with friends, or just a memorable experience, ICEBAR Orlando on International Drive is the perfect destination for a frozen adventure that you won\'t forget.', 'icebar/icebar1.jpg', '', 'icebar/icebar2.jpg', '', 'icebar/icebar3.jpg', '', 'icebar/icebar4.jpg', '', '8967 International Dr, Orlando, FL 32819', 'https://icebarorlando.com/', 'icebar/icebarmap.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/ICEBAR+Orlando/@28.434688,-81.473963,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m15!1m8!3m7!1s0x88e77e4b55c3eebb:0x378c4789fbc78caa!2sICEBAR+Orlando!8m2!3d28.434688!4d-81.4717743!10e1!16s%2Fm%2F0jl0ddq!3m5!1s0x88e77e4b55c3eebb:0x378c4789fbc78caa!8m2!3d28.434688!4d-81.4717743!16s%2Fm%2F0jl0ddq', 'ICEBAR Orlando is a unique bar experience featuring the largest permanent ice bar in the world - made entirely of ice from the far reaches of the Arctic Circle! ', '$$', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 21, 'Y', 'N', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', ''),
(22, 'Blue Martini Lounge Pointe Orlando', 'Blue Martini is a premier nightlife destination located on International Drive in Orlando, Florida. This sophisticated and stylish bar offers a unique experience, featuring live music, expertly crafted cocktails, and an elegant atmosphere that\'s perfect for a night out with friends.\r\n<br><br>\r\nAs you step inside Blue Martini, you\'ll immediately notice the sleek and stylish ambiance. The bar boasts plush seating, atmospheric lighting, and a spacious dance floor. The perfect place to unwind with friends, the bar also features a range of drinks, including signature cocktails, premium spirits, and wines.\r\n<br><br>\r\nBut what really sets Blue Martini apart is the live music. The bar has a rotating lineup of talented performers, playing everything from jazz and blues to top 40 hits. The music adds to the already vibrant atmosphere, creating an experience that\'s both lively and relaxing. The bar also hosts special events throughout the week, including ladies\' nights, happy hours, and theme nights.\r\n<br><br>\r\nWhile drinks and music are the main draw at Blue Martini, the bar also offers an impressive selection of small plates and appetizers. Whether you\'re in the mood for something savory like bacon-wrapped dates or something sweet like the signature chocolate fondue, the menu has something for everyone.\r\n<br><br>\r\nIt\'s no secret that Blue Martini is a favorite among celebrities and high-profile guests. Many come to enjoy the bar\'s upscale ambiance and impeccable service. It\'s not uncommon to spot a familiar face while enjoying a night out at this exclusive establishment.\r\n<br><br>\r\nIf you\'re looking for a nightlife destination that offers a unique and unforgettable experience, then look no further than Blue Martini on International Drive. Whether you\'re in the mood for live music, expertly crafted cocktails, or delicious small plates, this chic and sophisticated bar has it all.', 'blue/blue1.jpg', '', 'blue/blue2.jpg', '', 'blue/blue3.jpg', '', 'blue/blue4.jpg', '', '9101 International Dr #1182, Orlando, FL 32819', 'https://orlando.bluemartini.com/', 'blue/bluemap.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/Blue+Martini+Lounge+Pointe+Orlando/@28.4320453,-81.4875027,15z/data=!3m2!4b1!5s0x88e77e4b1da3fa15:0x7edf0a3a7257fc65!4m6!3m5!1s0x88e77ea893b83cbf:0x88385186aa88cea6!8m2!3d28.4320463!4d-81.4705939!16s%2Fg%2F1tmqmm1m', 'Blue Martini Lounge Pointe Orlando is a premier nightlife destination offering an upscale and stylish atmosphere for guests to enjoy delicious cocktails and delicious food.', '$$', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 21, 'Y', 'N', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', ''),
(23, 'Universal CityWalk Orlando', 'Universal CityWalk Orlando is the ultimate entertainment destination in Orlando. It\'s the perfect place for visitors to immerse themselves in the vibrant energy of the city and enjoy an array of dining, shopping, and entertainment options.\r\n<br><br>\r\nThe dining options at Universal CityWalk Orlando are sure to satisfy any craving. From classic American fare at Hard Rock Cafe to delicious sushi at The Cowfish, there\'s something for everyone. Visitors can also grab a drink at one of the many bars and lounges, such as the iconic Margaritaville or the high-energy Red Coconut Club.\r\n<br><br>\r\nThe shopping opportunities at Universal CityWalk Orlando are equally impressive. Visitors can find everything from unique souvenirs at the Universal Studios Store to designer brands at Fossil and Tommy Bahama. There are also specialty stores such as Quiet Flight Surf Shop and the NBA Store for sports fans.\r\n<br><br>\r\nBut perhaps the biggest draw of Universal CityWalk Orlando is the entertainment. Visitors can catch a movie at the AMC Universal Cineplex, laugh at the hilarious Blue Man Group, or enjoy live music at the Hard Rock Live venue. For those looking for a unique experience, they can try their hand at mini golf at Hollywood Drive-In Golf or ride the indoor skydiving simulator at iFLY.\r\n<br><br>\r\nUniversal CityWalk Orlando is open late, making it the perfect place for a night out on the town. Whether visitors are looking for a romantic evening or a fun night with friends, they\'ll find it all at this entertainment hub.\r\n<br><br>\r\nVisitors can also take advantage of Universal CityWalk Orlando\'s close proximity to Universal Studios Florida and Universal\'s Islands of Adventure, making it a convenient stop before or after a day at the theme parks. The CityWalk Orlando complex is easily accessible by car or the free shuttle service provided by Universal Orlando Resort.\r\n<br><br>\r\nOverall, Universal CityWalk Orlando is a must-visit destination for anyone looking for a fun and entertaining experience in Orlando.', 'citywalk/citywalk1.jpg', '', 'citywalk/citywalk2.jpg', '', 'citywalk/citywalk3.jpg', '', 'citywalk/citywalk4.jpg', '', '6000 Universal Blvd, Orlando, FL 32819', 'https://www.universalorlando.com/web/en/us/theme-parks/citywalk', 'citywalk/citywalkmap.jpg', 'citywalk/citywalkmap.jpg', 'Universal CityWalk Orlando is a vibrant entertainment complex featuring a wide variety of restaurants, bars, shops, and live entertainment, located just steps away from the exciting theme parks of Universal Orlando Resort. ', '0.00', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'N', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', ''),
(24, 'Disney Springs', 'Disney Spring is a premier shopping, dining, and entertainment district located at Walt Disney World Resort in Orlando, Florida. With its charming waterfront setting, Disney Springs offers something for everyone, from world-class restaurants and unique shopping experiences to live entertainment and family-friendly attractions.\r\n<br><br>\r\nDisney Springs features more than 150 retailers, including high-end brands such as Coach, Kate Spade, and Tiffany & Co. For those who prefer a more unique shopping experience, there are also specialty shops like The Art of Disney, Disney’s Days of Christmas, and The LEGO Store. Guests can also visit the newly expanded World of Disney store, which is the largest Disney merchandise store in the world.\r\n<br><br>\r\nFoodies will delight in the diverse array of dining options at Disney Springs, from celebrity chef restaurants like Wolfgang Puck Bar & Grill and Morimoto Asia to the popular food trucks and quick-service eateries at The Daily Poutine and Earl of Sandwich. And don\'t forget to visit The Boathouse, where guests can enjoy fresh seafood and take a ride on one of the amphicars, which are vintage vehicles that can drive on land and float on water.\r\n<br><br>\r\nLive entertainment is always on display at Disney Springs, with nightly shows featuring live music, dance performances, and even a virtual reality experience at The VOID. And for those who want to keep the fun going into the evening, there are a variety of nightlife options at Disney Springs, including the House of Blues and the Jock Lindsey’s Hangar Bar.\r\n<br><br>\r\nFamilies with young children can also enjoy the family-friendly attractions at Disney Springs, including the Marketplace Carousel and the LEGO Store’s Build and Play area.\r\n<br><br>\r\nDisney Springs is easily accessible from all Walt Disney World Resort hotels, with complimentary parking and transportation available. Whether you’re looking for a night out on the town or a day of shopping and entertainment, Disney Springs has it all.', 'springs/spring1.jpg', '', 'springs/spring2.jpg', '', 'springs/spring3.jpg', '', 'springs/spring4.jpg', '', '1486 Buena Vista Dr, Lake Buena Vista, FL 32830', 'https://www.disneysprings.com/', 'springs/springsmap.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/Disney+Springs/@28.3705684,-81.5215475,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m6!3m5!1s0x88dd7f8136a04afb:0x85a2c311efe17283!8m2!3d28.3705684!4d-81.5193588!16zL20vMDN0bWx6', 'Disney Springs is an exciting entertainment, dining and shopping complex at Walt Disney World Resort, featuring a variety of unique stores and restaurants, all set against a backdrop of iconic Disney characters and attractions. ', '0.00', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'N', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', ''),
(25, 'Jimmy Buffett\'s Margaritaville', 'Jimmy Buffett\'s Margaritaville is the ultimate destination for those seeking an island escape in the heart of Orlando. Our restaurant is inspired by the legendary singer-songwriter Jimmy Buffett, who is known for his laid-back, beachy vibe and signature song \"Margaritaville\".\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nAt our restaurant, you\'ll feel like you\'re on vacation as soon as you walk through the door. The atmosphere is vibrant and colorful, with tropical decor and island-inspired music playing in the background. Our friendly staff will greet you with a warm welcome and help you navigate our extensive menu, which features a variety of delicious dishes and refreshing drinks.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nOne of the highlights of our menu is, of course, our margaritas. We have a variety of flavors to choose from, including classic lime, strawberry, and mango. Our drinks are made with fresh ingredients and top-shelf tequila, so you know you\'re getting the best quality. We also have a selection of other cocktails, wine, and beer for those who prefer something different.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nWhen it comes to food, we have something for everyone. Our menu includes classic American dishes with a tropical twist, like our famous \"Cheeseburger in Paradise\" and \"Volcano Nachos\". We also have a variety of seafood options, like our \"Key West Grilled Shrimp\" and \"Boat Drinks Fish Tacos\". For those who prefer something lighter, we have a selection of salads and sandwiches.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nIn addition to our delicious food and drinks, we also have live entertainment on select nights. You can enjoy live music from local artists while sipping on a margarita and taking in the laid-back atmosphere.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nOverall, Jimmy Buffett\'s Margaritaville is the perfect destination for those looking for a fun and relaxing dining experience. Whether you\'re a longtime fan of Jimmy Buffett or just looking for a taste of the island life, we guarantee you\'ll leave feeling like you\'ve been on vacation. So come on in, grab a margarita, and let us transport you to paradise.\r\n', 'jimmybuffett/image1.jpeg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '6000 Universal Studios Plaza #704, Orlando, FL 32819', 'https://www.margaritavilleorlando.com/', '', '', 'Jimmy Buffett\'s Margaritaville is an iconic restaurant and bar, enjoy a variety of drinks and food inspired by the Caribbean, as well as live music and entertainment in a lively atmosphere.', '$$', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', ''),
(26, 'Antojitos Authentic Mexican Food', 'Antojitos Authentic Mexican Food is an amazing culinary destination for lovers of Mexican cuisine. Located in the heart of Orlando, this restaurant is perfect for those who want to experience authentic Mexican food and ambiance.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nAntojitos is known for its delicious menu that features a variety of traditional Mexican dishes with a modern twist. Whether you are looking for tacos, burritos, or enchiladas, you will find a wide selection of mouth-watering options that will satisfy your cravings. The restaurant also offers a great selection of cocktails and margaritas that complement the spicy flavors of the dishes.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nWhat sets Antojitos apart is its vibrant and colorful atmosphere that transports you to a Mexican fiesta. The interior of the restaurant is adorned with vibrant murals and decor inspired by the famous Mexican holiday, Dia de los Muertos. The restaurant also has a spacious outdoor patio area that is perfect for enjoying your meal while taking in the warm Florida weather.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nAntojitos is a great option for families, couples, and groups of friends who want to enjoy a fun and lively atmosphere while indulging in delicious food. The restaurant also hosts live music performances and other events that add to the festive ambiance.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nIf you are looking for a unique and authentic Mexican dining experience, Antojitos is definitely worth a visit. With its great food, lively atmosphere, and friendly staff, this restaurant is sure to become a favorite among locals and visitors alike. So come on down to Antojitos and get ready for a true Mexican culinary adventure!\r\n', 'antojitos/image1.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '6000 Universal Blvd, Orlando, FL 32819', 'https://www.universalorlando.com/web/en/us/things-to-do/dining/antojitos-authentic-mexican-food', '', '', 'Antojitos Authentic Mexican Food is an exciting and authentic Mexican restaurant located in Universal CityWalk Orlando. ', '$$', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', ''),
(27, 'The Toothsome Chocolate Emporium & Savory Feast Kitchen', 'The Toothsome Chocolate Emporium & Savory Feast Kitchen is a must-visit destination for all chocolate lovers visiting Orlando. Located in the heart of Universal CityWalk, this unique restaurant offers a one-of-a-kind dining experience that combines savory and sweet flavors with a steampunk-inspired atmosphere.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nUpon entering the restaurant, guests are transported to a world of chocolate and whimsy. The decor features gears, gadgets, and machinery, creating an immersive atmosphere that feels like a cross between a chocolate factory and a Victorian-era laboratory. The restaurant\'s centerpiece is a towering chocolate factory-themed bar, where guests can order a variety of chocolate-infused cocktails, milkshakes, and specialty drinks.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nBut the real star of the show at The Toothsome Chocolate Emporium is the food. The menu features a mix of classic American comfort food and international cuisine, with a focus on incorporating chocolate into unexpected dishes. Guests can enjoy dishes like the Chocolate Almond Bread Pudding French Toast, the Chicken Alfredo with White Chocolate Garlic Bread, and the Bacon Wrapped Pork Tenderloin with Chocolate Cherry BBQ Sauce.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nOf course, no visit to The Toothsome Chocolate Emporium would be complete without indulging in one of their decadent desserts. The restaurant offers an array of over-the-top milkshakes, including the Chocolate x5, a milkshake made with chocolate ice cream, chocolate chunks, chocolate sauce, whipped cream, and a chocolate-covered strawberry. The Emporium also features a variety of cakes, sundaes, and other chocolate creations that are sure to satisfy any sweet tooth.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nThe Toothsome Chocolate Emporium & Savory Feast Kitchen is a fun and unique destination that appeals to both adults and children. Families will love the whimsical atmosphere, while foodies will appreciate the creative and delicious menu. With its prime location in Universal CityWalk, The Toothsome Chocolate Emporium is a must-visit destination for anyone looking for a sweet and savory dining experience in Orlando.\r\n', 'toothsome/image1.jpeg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '6000 Universal Blvd, Orlando, FL 32819', 'https://www.universalorlando.com/web/en/us/things-to-do/dining/toothsome-chocolate-emporium-and-savory-feast-kitchen', '', '', 'Enjoy an indulgent feast of gourmet chocolates and decadent desserts, then sit back and relax in this steampunk-inspired restaurant.', '$$', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', ''),
(28, 'Bigfire', 'Bigfire is a unique dining destination that offers a rustic and cozy atmosphere with a modern twist. Located in Universal CityWalk Orlando, this restaurant serves up mouth-watering American fare with a focus on open-fire cooking techniques.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nUpon entering, you\'ll be greeted by a warm and inviting ambiance that\'s perfect for a romantic date night or a family dinner. The restaurant\'s design is inspired by the great outdoors, featuring reclaimed wood, stone, and metal accents throughout the space. The centerpiece of the restaurant is a large open-fire hearth, where chefs prepare dishes using various techniques such as smoking, grilling, and roasting.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nBigfire\'s menu showcases the best of American cuisine, with dishes ranging from classic comfort food to creative culinary innovations. Start your meal with an appetizer such as the house-smoked salmon dip or the charred octopus with chorizo and chimichurri. For the main course, try the signature Bigfire burger, a juicy patty topped with smoked gouda, crispy onions, and garlic aioli. If you\'re in the mood for something heartier, go for the 14 oz. prime ribeye steak, which is cooked to perfection over the open fire.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nAside from the delicious food, Bigfire also has an extensive drink menu featuring craft cocktails, local beers, and a wide selection of wine. The restaurant\'s mixologists create unique and flavorful cocktails that perfectly complement the dishes on the menu. The drinks are made with fresh ingredients and are expertly crafted to satisfy any palate.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nIf you\'re looking for a unique dining experience in Orlando, be sure to visit Bigfire. The restaurant\'s combination of delicious food, cozy atmosphere, and expertly crafted drinks make it the perfect spot for any occasion. Whether you\'re a foodie, a steak lover, or just looking for a fun night out, Bigfire is sure to exceed your expectations.\r\n', 'bigfire/image1.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '6000 Universal Blvd, Orlando, FL 32819', 'https://www.universalorlando.com/web/en/us/things-to-do/dining/bigfire', '', '', 'Enjoy a variety of classic dishes cooked over an open flame, paired with signature craft cocktails and an extensive wine list.', '$$', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', ''),
(29, 'VIVO Italian Kitchen', 'VIVO Italian Kitchen is a must-visit dining destination for anyone looking to experience delicious Italian cuisine in the heart of Orlando. This restaurant offers a unique twist on traditional Italian dishes, with a menu that is sure to satisfy any craving.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nFrom classic pasta dishes like spaghetti carbonara and lasagna to delicious pizzas and flatbreads, VIVO Italian Kitchen has something for everyone. Each dish is made with fresh, high-quality ingredients, and the chefs are committed to using traditional techniques to create authentic Italian flavors.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nThe restaurant\'s ambiance is warm and inviting, with a modern yet cozy interior that sets the perfect mood for a romantic dinner or a family-friendly meal. Whether you\'re looking for a casual night out with friends or a more formal dining experience, VIVO Italian Kitchen is the perfect spot.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nIn addition to the delicious food, VIVO Italian Kitchen also boasts an impressive wine list featuring a selection of Italian wines that pair perfectly with the menu. And for those looking for a refreshing cocktail, the restaurant\'s mixologists craft unique and creative drinks that are sure to please.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nOverall, VIVO Italian Kitchen is a must-visit for anyone looking to experience delicious Italian cuisine in Orlando. With its warm and inviting atmosphere, commitment to using high-quality ingredients, and a menu that is sure to satisfy any craving, this restaurant is a true gem in the city\'s dining scene. So if you\'re looking for an unforgettable dining experience in Orlando, be sure to add VIVO Italian Kitchen to your list.\r\n', 'vivo/image1.jpeg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '6000 Universal Blvd, Orlando, FL 32819', 'https://www.universalorlando.com/web/en/us/things-to-do/dining/vivo-italian-kitchen', '', '', 'Enjoy a variety of traditional Italian dishes prepared with the freshest ingredients, from classic pasta dishes to seafood specialties.', '$$', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', ''),
(30, 'Red Oven Pizza Bakery', 'Red Oven Pizza Bakery is a must-visit destination for pizza lovers and foodies alike. Located in the heart of Universal CityWalk Orlando, Red Oven Pizza Bakery serves up authentic, handcrafted pizzas with the freshest ingredients.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nRed Oven Pizza Bakery offers a unique and interactive dining experience where you can watch as skilled chefs prepare your pizza in a traditional wood-burning oven. From the classic Margherita to the meat lover\'s dream, there is a pizza for every taste preference. You can also create your own pizza with your favorite toppings.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nBut that\'s not all! Red Oven Pizza Bakery also offers a selection of salads, sandwiches, and desserts. Try the Burrata Caprese Salad, made with heirloom tomatoes, fresh basil, and creamy Burrata cheese, or the classic Italian sandwich, stacked high with meats, cheese, and vegetables.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nRed Oven Pizza Bakery has a welcoming and vibrant atmosphere, with indoor and outdoor seating available. The restaurant is also conveniently located near Universal Studios and Islands of Adventure, making it a perfect place to grab a quick bite before or after a day at the theme parks.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nDon\'t forget to check out the bar, which serves craft beers, wine, and cocktails, including the signature Blood Orange Margarita. The bar area also has flat-screen TVs, making it a great spot to catch up on sports or news.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nRed Oven Pizza Bakery is a great place for families, friends, and couples to enjoy delicious food and a fun atmosphere. With its prime location, friendly staff, and delicious food, it\'s no wonder why Red Oven Pizza Bakery is a top-rated destination for pizza lovers and foodies alike.\r\n', 'redoven/image1.jpeg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '6000 Universal Blvd, Orlando, FL 32819', 'https://www.universalorlando.com/web/en/us/things-to-do/dining/red-oven-pizza-bakery', '', '', 'Enjoy a variety of freshly made pizzas, calzones, and Italian-inspired dishes, all made with the freshest ingredients.', '$$', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', ''),
(31, 'Voodoo Doughnut', 'If you have a sweet tooth, then Voodoo Doughnut in Orlando is a must-visit attraction. This popular doughnut shop is known for its quirky and unique flavors, eye-catching decorations, and long lines of eager customers waiting to try their tasty treats.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nAt Voodoo Doughnut, you\'ll find a wide range of doughnuts with creative names like the Voodoo Doll, Bacon Maple Bar, and Old Dirty Bastard. They offer a variety of vegan and gluten-free options, as well as their signature \"cocktail\" doughnuts like the Margarita and the Cosmopolitan. Each doughnut is made fresh daily, and their skilled bakers take pride in using high-quality ingredients to ensure that every bite is packed with flavor.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nThe shop itself is just as entertaining as the doughnuts. With funky decor, colorful walls, and a lively atmosphere, it\'s the perfect spot to snap a few photos for your social media feed. Plus, you can watch the bakers in action as they make the doughnuts right in front of your eyes.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nVoodoo Doughnut is located at Universal CityWalk Orlando, which is easily accessible from most Orlando attractions. Whether you\'re taking a break from the theme parks or looking for a fun night out, this doughnut shop is a great choice. Plus, it\'s open late, so you can satisfy your cravings at any time of day or night.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nOverall, Voodoo Doughnut is a must-visit destination for anyone with a sweet tooth. Their unique flavors, fun atmosphere, and commitment to quality make them stand out from other doughnut shops in the area. So, be sure to stop by and try a few of their delicious treats on your next trip to Orlando.\r\n', 'voodoo/image1.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '6000 Universal Blvd, Orlando, FL 32819', 'https://www.voodoodoughnut.com/', '', '', 'Enjoy a variety of delicious and creative doughnuts, from the traditional favorites to the unique and inventive flavors. With its funky atmosphere and delicious treats, Voodoo Doughnut is the perfect place to satisfy your sweet tooth and have a bit of fun.', '$', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', ''),
(32, 'Hot Dog Hall of Fame', 'Looking for a quick bite to eat that\'s full of flavor and fun? Look no further than Hot Dog Hall of Fame! This casual eatery in Universal CityWalk Orlando is the perfect spot to grab a delicious hot dog or other classic American fare.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nAt Hot Dog Hall of Fame, you\'ll find an impressive selection of hot dogs, sausages, and toppings, all inspired by famous ballparks from around the country. Choose from classics like the Chicago dog, the New York dog, or the Detroit Coney dog, or try something a little more unique like the Texas dog with chili and cheddar cheese. All hot dogs are served on fresh buns and can be customized to your liking with a variety of toppings, including sauerkraut, onions, relish, and more.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nBut hot dogs aren\'t the only thing on the menu at Hot Dog Hall of Fame. You\'ll also find burgers, fries, onion rings, and even a few vegetarian options. Don\'t forget to wash it all down with a cold soda or beer.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nOne of the best things about Hot Dog Hall of Fame is the casual, laid-back atmosphere. Grab a table on the outdoor patio and enjoy people-watching while you chow down on your tasty hot dog. Inside, you\'ll find a fun, sports-themed decor that pays tribute to some of the greatest ballparks in the country.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nLocated in the heart of Universal CityWalk Orlando, Hot Dog Hall of Fame is the perfect spot to grab a quick and delicious meal before or after a day at the nearby theme parks. And with affordable prices and friendly service, it\'s a must-visit for any hot dog lover.\r\n', 'hotdoghof/image1.jpeg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '6000 Universal Blvd, Orlando, FL 32819', 'https://www.universalorlando.com/web/en/us/things-to-do/dining/hot-dog-hall-of-fame', '', '', 'Hot Dog Hall of Fame is a unique fast-food eatery located in Universal CityWalk Orlando. Enjoy a selection of freshly grilled hot dogs, sausages, and other classic American favorites, all made with the highest quality ingredients.', '$', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', ''),
(33, 'Bread Box Handcrafted Sandwiches', 'Bread Box Handcrafted Sandwiches is a must-visit restaurant in Orlando, Florida for sandwich lovers. With a rustic atmosphere and a menu filled with unique sandwich creations, it\'s the perfect spot for a quick and satisfying lunch or dinner.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nLocated in the heart of the bustling Universal CityWalk, Bread Box is a popular destination for both tourists and locals. The menu features a variety of sandwiches made with fresh, locally sourced ingredients, including classic options like grilled cheese and BLT, as well as more inventive creations like the Pimento Cheese and Bacon sandwich or the Turkey, Brie and Raspberry jam sandwich.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nIn addition to the delicious sandwiches, Bread Box also offers sides such as hand-cut fries, tater tots, and house-made chips. The restaurant also features a rotating selection of craft beers and seasonal cocktails, making it a great spot for a quick bite or a relaxed evening out.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nThe interior of the restaurant is designed with a charming vintage feel, featuring exposed brick walls, rustic wooden tables, and a tin ceiling. The casual atmosphere is perfect for families, couples, or solo diners looking for a relaxed and welcoming dining experience.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nWhether you\'re in the mood for a classic sandwich or something a bit more unique, Bread Box Handcrafted Sandwiches has something to offer. With friendly service, a great location, and delicious food, it\'s a top choice for anyone visiting the Orlando area.\r\n', 'breadbox/image1.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '6000 Universal Blvd, Orlando, FL 32819', 'https://www.universalorlando.com/web/en/us/things-to-do/dining/bread-box-handcrafted-sandwiches', '', '', 'Bread Box Handcrafted Sandwiches is a unique sandwich shop located in Universal CityWalk Orlando. Enjoy a variety of freshly made sandwiches, salads, and sides, all crafted with the freshest ingredients.', '$', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', ''),
(34, 'Chef Art Smith\'s Homecomin\'', 'Welcome to Chef Art Smith\'s Homecomin\' is a cozy and inviting restaurant that serves up classic Southern comfort food with a modern twist. Located in the heart of Disney Springs, Chef Art Smith\'s Homecomin\' is the perfect spot for travelers looking for a taste of the South.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nThe menu features a wide variety of Southern dishes, including fried chicken, biscuits, mac and cheese, and collard greens. All ingredients are sourced locally and seasonally, ensuring that every dish is fresh and delicious. Chef Art Smith is a James Beard Award-winning chef who has appeared on Top Chef Masters and Iron Chef America, so you know you\'re in good hands.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nIn addition to the food, Chef Art Smith\'s Homecomin\' also boasts a great selection of cocktails, wine, and beer. Be sure to try one of their signature drinks, like the Shine Margarita or the Florida Mule, which features Florida orange vodka and ginger beer.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nThe atmosphere of Chef Art Smith\'s Homecomin\' is warm and welcoming, with a cozy dining room and outdoor seating area. The restaurant also has a gift shop where you can pick up souvenirs and food items to take home with you.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nIf you\'re looking for a unique dining experience with delicious Southern food, Chef Art Smith\'s Homecomin\' is a must-visit. Whether you\'re coming for lunch, dinner, or brunch, you\'re sure to leave satisfied and with a newfound love for Southern cuisine. Don\'t forget to make a reservation to ensure you get a table at this popular spot!\r\n', 'chefartsmith/image1.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '1602 E Buena Vista Dr, Lake Buena Vista, FL 32830', 'https://disneyworld.disney.go.com/dining/disney-springs/chef-art-smiths-homecomin/', '', '', 'Chef Art Smith\'s Homecomin\' is a modern American restaurant that offers a unique dining experience with its Southern-style comfort food, from home-style dishes to classic Gulf Coast seafood.', '$$', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', '');
