(35, 'Orlando Eye', 'Orlando Eye is one of the city\'s most iconic attractions and a must-visit destination for any visitor to the Orlando area. Located on International Drive, the Orlando Eye is a 400-foot-tall observation wheel that offers stunning panoramic views of the surrounding area.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nThe Orlando Eye opened in 2015 and has since become one of the most popular attractions in the Orlando area. The observation wheel features 30 air-conditioned capsules, each of which can hold up to 15 people. Visitors can enjoy a peaceful and scenic 20-minute ride on the Orlando Eye, taking in the breathtaking views of downtown Orlando, the theme parks, and the surrounding natural beauty.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nIn addition to the observation wheel, the Orlando Eye complex also features several other attractions and experiences. The SEA LIFE Orlando Aquarium, located at the base of the Orlando Eye, allows visitors to explore a variety of underwater habitats and marine creatures, including sharks, stingrays, and sea turtles. There\'s also the Madame Tussauds Orlando, a world-famous wax museum that features lifelike sculptures of celebrities, historical figures, and fictional characters.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nThe Orlando Eye complex offers several dining and shopping options for visitors. The Wheelhouse Market is a food hall featuring a variety of vendors and cuisine options, while the Sugar Factory American Brasserie offers sweet treats and cocktails. The complex also features several retail shops where visitors can purchase souvenirs and gifts.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nTo make the most of your visit to the Orlando Eye, it\'s important to plan ahead and consider factors such as wait times, weather conditions, and special events. It\'s recommended to purchase tickets in advance to avoid long lines, especially during peak tourist season. Additionally, be sure to check the weather forecast and dress appropriately for the conditions, as the observation wheel is open rain or shine. Visitors can also consider purchasing combination tickets that include admission to other nearby attractions, such as the SEA LIFE Orlando Aquarium and Madame Tussauds Orlando.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nIn conclusion, the Orlando Eye is a must-visit attraction for anyone visiting the Orlando area. With its stunning views, unique attractions, and convenient location, the Orlando Eye offers visitors an unforgettable experience that is sure to leave a lasting impression.\r\n', 'orlandoeye/image1.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '8375 International Dr, Orlando, FL 32819', 'https://iconparkorlando.com/', '', '', 'The Orlando Eye is a 400ft tall observation wheel located in ICON Park, offering stunning views of the city.', '27.99', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', ''),
(36, 'ICON Park', 'Icon Park is a dynamic entertainment complex located in the heart of Orlando\'s vibrant International Drive. Boasting a variety of attractions, from exhilarating rides to delectable dining options and incredible views, Icon Park has something to offer every type of visitor.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nOne of the most iconic attractions at Icon Park is The Wheel, a 400-foot tall observation wheel offering breathtaking views of the Orlando skyline. With 30 air-conditioned capsules, each accommodating up to 15 people, The Wheel is the perfect activity for families or large groups of friends. As you ascend to the top of the wheel, you\'ll be treated to panoramic views of the city and beyond.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nIn addition to The Wheel, Icon Park offers a plethora of other exciting attractions for visitors to enjoy. Thrill-seekers can experience the rush of the Orlando StarFlyer, a 450-foot tall swing ride that provides stunning views of the city. The complex also features a variety of other rides and activities, including a 7D Dark Ride Adventure and an arcade.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nFoodies will be delighted by the diverse dining options available at Icon Park. From classic American cuisine to international flavors, the complex has a variety of restaurants and eateries to suit every taste and budget. Whether you\'re looking for a quick snack or a full meal, you\'ll find something delicious to indulge in at Icon Park.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nOne of the highlights of Icon Park is its lively atmosphere. The complex is always buzzing with energy, with street performers, live music, and other entertainment options to keep visitors entertained throughout the day. It\'s the perfect place to spend quality time with family or friends, soaking up the vibrant atmosphere of Orlando\'s entertainment district.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nOverall, Icon Park is a must-see destination for anyone visiting Orlando. With its diverse range of attractions, dining options, and stunning views, there\'s something for everyone to enjoy. Whether you\'re looking to take in the sights from The Wheel, experience the thrill of the StarFlyer, or simply relax and enjoy the lively atmosphere, Icon Park is the perfect destination for a day out in Orlando.\r\n\r\n', 'iconpark/image1.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '8375 International Dr, Orlando, FL 32819', 'https://iconparkorlando.com/', '', '', 'ICON Park is an exciting entertainment destination in Orlando, featuring unique attractions, delicious restaurants, and fun-filled activities for the whole family.', '', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'N', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', ''),
(37, 'Keg Social', 'Located in the Waterford Lakes area in Orlando, Keg Social is a must-visit destination for anyone looking for a fun and unique entertainment experience. With its extensive selection of craft beer, classic arcade games, and delicious food, Keg Social has something to offer for visitors of all ages.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nAs you enter Keg Social, you\'ll be immediately drawn to its impressive tap wall, which boasts over 60 beers on tap. From local brews to international favorites, the beer selection at Keg Social is unmatched. Whether you\'re a seasoned beer connoisseur or just looking to try something new, there\'s a beer for everyone to enjoy.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nKeg Social has an extensive collection of classic arcade games. The venue is home to a wide range of games, from retro favorites like Pac-Man and Donkey Kong to newer titles like Mario Kart and NBA Jam. Visitors can enjoy unlimited game play for a flat fee, making Keg Social the perfect destination for an evening of fun and nostalgia.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nWhen it comes to food, Keg Social doesn\'t disappoint. The menu features classic pub fare with a modern twist, offering a variety of shareable appetizers like loaded tater tots and bacon-wrapped jalapeños. For main courses, visitors can choose from a variety of burgers, sandwiches, and salads, all made with high-quality ingredients and served fresh.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nIn addition to its impressive beer selection, classic arcade games, and delicious food, Keg Social also offers a variety of events and promotions throughout the week. From trivia nights to karaoke parties, there\'s always something happening at Keg Social. Be sure to check the venue\'s website or social media pages for the latest event schedule.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nOverall, Keg Social is a fun and exciting destination for visitors looking for a unique entertainment experience in Orlando. With its extensive beer selection, classic arcade games, and delicious food, Keg Social has something for everyone to enjoy. Whether you\'re looking for a night out with friends or a fun family outing, Keg Social is the perfect destination for a memorable evening in Orlando.\r\n\r\n', 'kegsocial/image1.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '12850 Waterford Lakes Pkwy, Orlando, FL 32828', 'https://keg.social/', '', '', 'Keg Social Orlando is a lively bar and lounge offering craft beer, wine, and cocktails. Enjoy live music and DJs, as well as a wide range of activities like bowling, billiards, arcade, and axe throwing.', '$$', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 21, 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', ''),
(38, 'Boardwalk Bowl Entertainment Center', 'Boardwalk Bowl Entertainment Center is one of the most exciting and vibrant destinations in the Orlando area. Located on East Colonial Drive, the Boardwalk Bowl Entertainment Center is a premier bowling and entertainment venue that offers visitors a wide range of activities and amenities.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nThe Boardwalk Bowl Entertainment Center features a state-of-the-art bowling alley with 80 lanes, making it one of the largest in the state of Florida. Visitors can enjoy a fun and competitive game of bowling with family and friends, with amenities such as automatic scoring, bumper lanes, and ball ramps available for younger or less experienced bowlers. The venue also features a large arcade area with a variety of classic and modern games, including virtual reality experiences and prize redemption options.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nThe Boardwalk Bowl Entertainment Center has several dining and drinking options for visitors to enjoy. The lively Bowlers\' Lounge is a full-service sports bar with a variety of food and beverage options, including craft beers, cocktails, and a menu featuring pub favorites such as burgers, wings, and nachos. The venue also features a Pizza Pub restaurant, which serves delicious hand-tossed pizzas, salads, and other Italian favorites.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nThe Boardwalk Bowl Entertainment Center is a popular destination for birthday parties, corporate events, and other special occasions. The venue offers customizable party packages that include bowling, arcade games, and catering options, as well as private rooms and event spaces for larger gatherings. Additionally, the Boardwalk Bowl Entertainment Center hosts regular events and promotions, such as weekly bowling leagues, trivia nights, and holiday-themed parties.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nTo make the most of your visit to the Boardwalk Bowl Entertainment Center, it\'s important to plan ahead and consider factors such as wait times, special events, and parking options. The venue is open seven days a week, with extended hours on weekends and holidays. Visitors can purchase tickets and reserve lanes online in advance to avoid wait times, and should plan to arrive early to secure parking in the venue\'s ample lot.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nIn conclusion, the Boardwalk Bowl Entertainment Center is a premier destination for anyone looking for a fun and exciting activity in the Orlando area. With its top-notch bowling facilities, vibrant arcade area, and delicious dining and drinking options, the Boardwalk Bowl Entertainment Center offers something for everyone, making it a must-visit destination for visitors of all ages.\r\n', 'boardwalkbowl/image1.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '10749 E Colonial Dr, Orlando, FL 32817', 'https://www.alomabowlingcenters.com/boardwalk/', '', '', 'Boardwalk Bowl Entertainment Center is a family-friendly fun center with bowling, laser tag, arcade games, and karaoke. Also enjoy great food and drinks on a night out with friends or a family outing!', '$$', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'Age requirement becomes 21+ after 9PM'),
(39, 'Aloma Bowl', 'Aloma Bowl is one of the premier entertainment destinations in Winter Park, Florida. Whether you\'re a seasoned bowler or looking for a fun activity to enjoy with family and friends, Aloma Bowl has something for everyone.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nAloma Bowl boasts a state-of-the-art bowling alley with 32 lanes, automatic scoring, and a variety of bowling balls to choose from. The venue offers a fun and competitive atmosphere that is perfect for both serious bowlers and those just looking to have some fun. The venue also features an arcade area with a variety of classic and modern games, including air hockey, basketball, and skee-ball.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nWhen you need to take a break from bowling or arcade games, Aloma Bowl has several dining and drinking options to choose from. The venue\'s on-site restaurant, The Grille at Aloma Bowl, offers a variety of food and beverage options, including burgers, wings, salads, and pizzas. The restaurant also has a full bar, with a variety of beer, wine, and cocktail options available.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nAloma Bowl is the perfect place to host your next special event or party. The venue offers customizable party packages that include bowling, arcade games, and catering options. Whether you\'re hosting a birthday party, corporate event, or just a fun night out with friends, Aloma Bowl has everything you need to make your event a success.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nTo make the most of your visit to Aloma Bowl, it\'s important to plan ahead and consider factors such as wait times, special events, and parking options. The venue is open seven days a week, with extended hours on weekends and holidays. Visitors can purchase tickets and reserve lanes online in advance to avoid wait times, and should plan to arrive early to secure parking in the venue\'s ample lot.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nIn conclusion, Aloma Bowl is a top-notch entertainment destination that offers visitors a fun and competitive atmosphere, delicious dining options, and a variety of special event packages. With its state-of-the-art bowling facilities, vibrant arcade area, and welcoming atmosphere, Aloma Bowl is a must-visit destination for anyone looking for a fun and memorable experience in Winter Park.\r\n', 'alomabowl/image1.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '2530 Aloma Ave, Winter Park, FL 32792', 'https://www.alomabowlingcenters.com/aloma/', '', '', 'Aloma Bowl is a family-friendly bowling alley in Orlando, offering 48 lanes, bumper lanes for kids, and a full-service snack bar. Enjoy a night of fun with friends and family at Aloma Bowl!', '$$', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', ''),
(40, 'Congo River Golf', 'Located just off International Drive, Congo River Golf is an exciting and adventurous miniature golf course that offers visitors an immersive experience into the wilds of Africa. From the moment you step into the course, you\'ll be transported into a lush and vibrant jungle filled with exotic animals, challenging obstacles, and beautiful waterfalls.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nOne of the standout features of Congo River Golf is its beautifully landscaped course. The course is filled with lush greenery, cascading waterfalls, and winding streams that create a serene and peaceful atmosphere. At the same time, the course is also filled with challenging obstacles and tricky holes that will test your skills and keep you entertained.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nCongo River Golf is more than just a miniature golf course. It also features a variety of other attractions that will keep visitors entertained for hours. The venue is home to a giant arcade, where visitors can play a wide range of games and win prizes. There\'s also a gem mining station, where visitors can try their hand at mining for gems and fossils.\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nOne of the highlights of Congo River Golf is its animal exhibit, where visitors can get up close and personal with a variety of exotic animals. From baby alligators to snakes and birds, the animal exhibit is a unique and educational experience that visitors of all ages will enjoy. There\'s also a giant snake statue that visitors can take pictures with.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nCongo River Golf is a popular destination for families, and it\'s easy to see why. The course is designed to be fun and engaging for visitors of all ages, with a variety of obstacles and challenges that will keep everyone entertained. The venue also offers birthday packages, group rates, and other special promotions that make it an affordable and enjoyable destination for families.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nCongo River Golf is an exciting and adventurous destination for visitors looking for a fun and unique experience in Orlando. With its beautifully landscaped course, challenging obstacles, and exotic animal exhibit, Congo River Golf is a must-visit destination for families and anyone looking for a fun day out. Whether you\'re a seasoned golfer or just looking for a fun and relaxing activity, Congo River Golf is the perfect destination for a memorable day in Orlando.\r\n\r\n', 'congoriver/image1.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '5901 International Dr, Orlando, FL 32819', 'https://www.congoriver.com/', '', '', 'Congo River Golf is an award-winning miniature golf course that offers a unique and exciting experience with its nine-hole adventure course and hidden caves, waterfalls, and other exciting features.', '15.49', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'N', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', ''),
(41, 'Lake Eola Park', 'Lake Eola Park is one of the most picturesque parks in the heart of downtown Orlando. This urban oasis offers visitors a chance to escape the hustle and bustle of the city and enjoy a peaceful stroll around the lake or a picnic with family and friends.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nLake Eola Park is a 43-acre public park located in the heart of downtown Orlando, with a large lake at its center. The park features a paved walkway that encircles the lake, providing visitors with a scenic view of the city skyline. In addition to the walkway, the park also boasts a variety of amenities, including a playground, swan boat rentals, picnic areas, and a popular Sunday farmer\'s market.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nLake Eola Park offers a wide range of activities for visitors of all ages. Whether you\'re looking to take a leisurely stroll around the lake or get active with a game of frisbee or volleyball, there\'s something for everyone. Swan boat rentals are a popular attraction, allowing visitors to paddle around the lake and take in the stunning views. The park is also a popular spot for outdoor yoga and fitness classes, which are offered throughout the year.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nThroughout the year, Lake Eola Park hosts a variety of events and festivals, including concerts, food and wine festivals, and cultural celebrations. One of the most popular events is the annual Orlando International Dragon Boat Festival, where teams race traditional Chinese dragon boats on the lake. The park is also home to the iconic Lake Eola Fountain, which is lit up with different colors during special events and holidays.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nLake Eola Park is open seven days a week from 6am to midnight, with free admission for all visitors. Parking can be found in nearby garages and on the street, but can be limited during peak hours and events. Visitors should also plan to bring sunscreen and water, as there are limited vending options within the park.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nIn conclusion, Lake Eola Park is a must-visit destination for anyone looking to escape the city and enjoy a peaceful stroll or fun-filled day with family and friends. With its stunning views, wide range of activities, and lively events calendar, Lake Eola Park is a true gem in the heart of downtown Orlando.\r\n', 'lakeeola/image1.jpeg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Downtown Orlando - Lake Eola', 'https://www.orlando.gov/Parks-the-Environment/Directory/Lake-Eola-Park', '', '', 'Lake Eola Park is a picturesque park in downtown Orlando, Florida, featuring a large lake, walking paths, a swan boat ride, and a variety of other attractions.', '0', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'N', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', ''),
(42, 'Wekiwa Springs State Park', 'Wekiwa Springs State Park is a beautiful natural oasis located just north of Orlando. This stunning park offers visitors a chance to escape the city and immerse themselves in the beauty of Florida\'s natural landscape.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nWekiwa Springs State Park covers over 7,000 acres of lush vegetation and crystal-clear springs. The park is home to a variety of wildlife, including deer, otters, and alligators. Visitors can explore the park\'s hiking trails, paddle along the Wekiva River, swim in the springs, or simply relax in a peaceful natural setting.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nWekiwa Springs State Park offers a wide range of activities for visitors to enjoy. One of the most popular attractions is swimming in the park\'s crystal-clear springs, which are consistently 72 degrees Fahrenheit year-round. Visitors can also rent canoes, kayaks, and paddleboards to explore the Wekiva River, which runs through the park. The park also features over 13 miles of hiking trails, ranging from easy to challenging, with stunning views of the park\'s natural beauty.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nFor those looking to extend their stay, Wekiwa Springs State Park offers a variety of camping options. The park features 60 campsites, including primitive sites, tent sites, and RV sites with electric and water hookups. The campground offers amenities such as restrooms, showers, and a dump station. Campsites are available for reservations, and visitors are encouraged to book early during peak seasons.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nWekiwa Springs State Park is open seven days a week from 8am to sunset, with an entrance fee of $6 per vehicle. Visitors should plan to bring sunscreen, bug spray, and water, as there are limited vending options within the park. Pets are welcome in designated areas of the park, but visitors should review the park\'s pet policy before bringing their furry friends.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nIn conclusion, Wekiwa Springs State Park is a stunning natural destination that offers visitors a chance to escape the city and immerse themselves in Florida\'s natural beauty. With its crystal-clear springs, scenic hiking trails, and peaceful camping options, Wekiwa Springs State Park is a must-visit destination for nature lovers and outdoor enthusiasts.\r\n', 'wekiwapark/image1.jpeg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '1800 Wekiwa Cir, Apopka, FL 32712', 'https://www.floridastateparks.org/parks-and-trails/wekiwa-springs-state-park', '', '', 'Wekiwa Springs State Park is a beautiful park located in Apopka, Florida, featuring crystal-clear springs, a large lake, and miles of trails for hiking, biking, and wildlife watching.', '6', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'N', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', ''),
(43, 'Central Florida Zoo & Botanical Gardens', 'Central Florida Zoo & Botanical Gardens is a beautiful and educational destination located in Sanford, Florida. This unique zoo offers visitors a chance to see a wide variety of animals from around the world, as well as explore stunning botanical gardens.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nThe Central Florida Zoo & Botanical Gardens is home to over 350 animals from over 100 different species. Visitors can see animals such as cheetahs, zebras, giraffes, and rhinos in the savanna exhibit, or watch playful otters and lemurs at the Rainforest Revealed exhibit. The zoo also features a petting zoo where visitors can interact with domestic animals such as goats and pigs. For an even closer look at some of the zoo\'s animals, visitors can participate in animal encounters or behind-the-scenes tours.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nIn addition to its impressive animal collection, the Central Florida Zoo & Botanical Gardens boasts over 100 acres of stunning botanical gardens. Visitors can stroll through the gardens and enjoy the sights and smells of a variety of plants and flowers from around the world. The gardens feature themed areas such as the butterfly garden, the bamboo garden, and the herb garden. Visitors can also learn about the importance of conservation and sustainable gardening practices at the Sustainable Agriculture and Conservation exhibit.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nThe Central Florida Zoo & Botanical Gardens hosts a variety of events throughout the year, including family-friendly activities, holiday-themed events, and fundraising events. One of the most popular events is the annual Zoo Boo Bash, a Halloween-themed event featuring trick-or-treating, haunted houses, and animal encounters. The zoo also offers educational programs and camps for children and adults, including behind-the-scenes tours and conservation programs.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nThe Central Florida Zoo & Botanical Gardens is open seven days a week from 9am to 3pm, with an entrance fee of $19.50 for adults and $13.75 for children. Visitors should plan to wear comfortable shoes and bring sunscreen and insect repellent. The zoo offers a variety of food and beverage options, as well as a gift shop with souvenirs and gifts.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nIn conclusion, the Central Florida Zoo & Botanical Gardens is a unique and educational destination that offers visitors a chance to see a wide variety of animals and explore stunning botanical gardens. With its exciting animal encounters, beautiful gardens, and fun events, the Central Florida Zoo & Botanical Gardens is a must-visit destination for families and nature lovers.\r\n', 'centralfloridazoo/image1.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '3755 W Seminole Blvd, Sanford, FL 32771', 'https://www.centralfloridazoo.org/', '', '', 'Central Florida Zoo & Botanical Gardens is a family-friendly attraction located in Sanford, Florida, featuring a variety of animals, lush gardens, and interactive educational programs.', '21.95', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'N', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'N', ''),
(44, 'Topgolf', 'Topgolf is a premier entertainment destination that combines the game of golf with high-tech gameplay, great food and drinks, and a lively social atmosphere. Topgolf venues are located in major cities throughout the United States and around the world, providing a unique experience for golfers and non-golfers alike.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nUpon entering a Topgolf venue, visitors are greeted by an impressive, multi-story driving range with numerous hitting bays. Each bay is equipped with microchipped golf balls that track the distance and accuracy of each shot hit. Scores are displayed on a personal screen in each bay and are used to compete against friends, family, or other players.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nTopgolf offers a variety of games and challenges that can be played using the microchipped golf balls. Visitors can test their accuracy with Topgolf\'s signature game, which awards points based on how close the ball lands to designated targets on the driving range. Other games include long drive contests, virtual golf on famous courses around the world, and even zombie-themed games.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nIn addition to the driving range and games, Topgolf venues also offer delicious food and drinks. Guests can enjoy a range of menu items from small bites to full entrees, including items such as crispy chicken wings, loaded nachos, and signature burgers. Topgolf also offers a variety of beverages, including craft beers, specialty cocktails, and non-alcoholic options.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nTopgolf\'s social atmosphere makes it the perfect destination for groups of friends, family outings, corporate events, and parties. Topgolf venues often feature live music, and their lively atmosphere is perfect for celebrations of all kinds.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nTopgolf is also committed to sustainability and is dedicated to reducing their carbon footprint. They use environmentally-friendly materials and energy-efficient equipment and have implemented recycling and composting programs.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nIn conclusion, Topgolf offers a unique and exciting way to enjoy the game of golf while also providing a social atmosphere, great food and drinks, and high-tech gameplay. Whether you\'re a seasoned golfer or a newcomer to the game, Topgolf provides a fun and memorable experience for everyone.\r\n\r\n', 'topgolf/image1.jpeg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '9295 Universal Blvd, Orlando, FL 32819', 'https://topgolf.com/us/orlando/', '', '', 'Topgolf is an exciting golf entertainment complex located in Orlando, Florida, featuring a state-of-the-art driving range, high-tech gaming, and a wide variety of food and drinks.', '60.00', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'N', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', ''),
(45, 'Kennedy Space Center Visitor Complex', 'Kennedy Space Center Visitor Complex is the gateway to exploring space and the history of NASA\'s space program. Located on the east coast of Florida, the Kennedy Space Center Visitor Complex is a must-visit destination for anyone interested in space exploration, science, and technology.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nThe Kennedy Space Center Visitor Complex features a variety of exhibits and attractions that offer visitors an interactive and immersive experience. Visitors can explore the Space Shuttle Atlantis exhibit, which houses the actual Space Shuttle Atlantis, as well as other space artifacts and interactive exhibits. Visitors can also experience what it\'s like to be an astronaut on the Shuttle Launch Experience, a simulated ride that takes guests on a thrilling journey to space.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nThe Kennedy Space Center Visitor Complex offers a variety of tours that take visitors behind the scenes of NASA\'s space program. Visitors can take the NASA Up-Close Tour, which provides a close-up view of the launch pads, Vehicle Assembly Building, and the Launch Control Center. Visitors can also take the Cape Canaveral Early Space Tour, which explores the early history of NASA\'s space program.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nThe Kennedy Space Center Visitor Complex offers a variety of educational programs for visitors of all ages. The complex hosts workshops and classes on topics such as space exploration, robotics, and engineering. Visitors can also participate in the Astronaut Training Experience, a program that simulates astronaut training and provides hands-on experience with space technology.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nThe Kennedy Space Center Visitor Complex is open seven days a week from 9am to 5pm. Admission is $57 for adults and $47 for children aged 3-11. Children under 3 are free. The complex is wheelchair accessible, and visitors can rent wheelchairs and strollers if needed. Visitors should wear comfortable shoes and bring sunscreen and a hat for the outdoor areas. The complex also has a gift shop and several restaurants that serve a variety of food and refreshments.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nIn conclusion, the Kennedy Space Center Visitor Complex is a unique and exciting destination that offers visitors a chance to explore the history of NASA\'s space program and learn about the science and technology behind space exploration. With its interactive exhibits, behind-the-scenes tours, and educational programs, the Kennedy Space Center Visitor Complex is a must-visit destination for anyone interested in space and science.\r\n', 'kennedyspace/image1.jpeg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Space Commerce Way, Merritt Island, FL 32953', 'https://www.kennedyspacecenter.com/', '', '', 'Discover the wonder of space at Kennedy Space Center Visitor Complex! Explore interactive exhibits, meet astronauts, and see historic spacecraft. Book your tickets today for an unforgettable experience.', '75.00', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', ''),
(46, 'Orlando Museum of Art', 'If you\'re a fan of art and culture, the Orlando Museum of Art should definitely be on your itinerary when visiting Orlando. This world-class museum features a diverse collection of artwork from across the globe, with a particular emphasis on contemporary American art.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nThe museum is housed in a beautiful building that is itself a work of art. The sleek, modern design of the building is complemented by the beautiful sculpture garden and outdoor spaces that surround it. Inside, you\'ll find a wide variety of galleries, each showcasing a different aspect of the museum\'s collection.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nOne of the museum\'s highlights is its extensive collection of American art from the 19th and 20th centuries. Here, you can view works by some of the most celebrated American artists, including Georgia O\'Keeffe, Grant Wood, and Edward Hopper. Other galleries feature contemporary art, African art, and art from Asia and the Pacific.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nThe museum also offers a range of educational programs and events. You can take part in guided tours, attend lectures and artist talks, or participate in workshops and classes. If you\'re traveling with kids, be sure to check out the museum\'s family programs, which are designed to engage young visitors with the world of art.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nFinally, don\'t forget to visit the museum\'s gift shop before you leave. Here, you\'ll find a great selection of books, art supplies, and unique gifts and souvenirs that are sure to please any art lover.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nOverall, the Orlando Museum of Art is a must-see destination for anyone interested in art and culture. With its impressive collection, beautiful setting, and engaging educational programs, it offers a world-class experience that is sure to be a highlight of your visit to Orlando.\r\n', 'orlandomuseumofart/image1.jpeg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '2416 N Mills Ave, Orlando, FL 32803', 'https://omart.org/', '', '', 'Immerse yourself in a world of art at the Orlando Museum of Art. From contemporary to classic, our collection showcases the beauty and diversity of human creativity. Plan your visit today and experience the wonder of art.', '20.00', 'T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'Y', 'N', ''),
(47, 'Madame Tussauds Orlando', 'Madame Tussauds Orlando is an immersive museum experience that allows you to get up close and personal with some of the most famous people in the world. From movie stars and musicians to politicians and athletes, you\'ll have the chance to take photos with incredibly lifelike wax figures of some of your favorite celebrities.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nOne of the things that sets Madame Tussauds apart from other museums is the level of interactivity it offers. Rather than simply viewing the wax figures from a distance, you can pose with them, touch them, and even put on costumes and props to create your own unique photo opportunities. Whether you want to take a selfie with Beyoncé or pretend to spar with Muhammad Ali, the possibilities are endless.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nThe museum is divided into several themed areas, each featuring its own collection of wax figures. For example, in the A-List Party section, you\'ll find figures of Hollywood stars like Leonardo DiCaprio and Angelina Jolie, while in the Justice League area, you can pose with the likes of Batman, Wonder Woman, and Superman. Other areas focus on sports stars, historical figures, and even popular TV characters.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nIn addition to the wax figures themselves, Madame Tussauds Orlando also features a range of multimedia exhibits and interactive displays. These provide interesting background information on the celebrities and events that the wax figures represent, as well as opportunities to test your knowledge with trivia games and other challenges.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nOverall, Madame Tussauds Orlando is a fun and unique attraction that offers something for visitors of all ages. Whether you\'re a die-hard fan of a particular celebrity or just looking for a fun photo opportunity, this museum is sure to be a highlight of your trip to Orlando. So why not add it to your itinerary today?\r\n', 'madametussauds/image.jpeg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '8387 International Dr, Orlando, FL 32819', 'https://www.madametussauds.com/orlando/', '', '', 'Step into the world of glamour and fame at Madame Tussauds Orlando! Our lifelike wax figures of celebrities, historical icons, and cultural icons are a must-see attraction. Book your tickets today and experience the thrill of being up close and personal with the stars.', '34.99', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'Y', 'Y', ''),
(48, 'Orlando International Premium Outlets', 'Located just minutes from the theme parks and downtown Orlando, Orlando Premium Outlets is a shopper\'s paradise. With over 160 stores featuring top brands and designer labels, this outdoor shopping center offers visitors an incredible shopping experience in a beautiful and convenient setting.\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nWhen you get to Orlando Premium Outlets, you\'ll find a stunning outdoor mall filled with lush landscaping, fountains, and palm trees. The open-air layout of the shopping center makes for a pleasant shopping experience, especially on a beautiful day. You\'ll find a wide range of stores here, from high-end fashion boutiques to popular retailers like Nike, Coach, and Michael Kors.\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nOrlando Premium Outlets is also known for its incredible deals and discounts. Many of the stores offer deep discounts on designer goods, making it the perfect destination for savvy shoppers looking to save money on high-end fashion. In addition, the shopping center offers a VIP Shopper Club, which gives visitors access to exclusive deals and coupons.\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nAside from shopping, Orlando Premium Outlets also offers a variety of dining options for visitors. The food court features a wide range of options, from fast food to sit-down restaurants, making it easy to refuel during a busy day of shopping. In addition, there are several outdoor seating areas where visitors can enjoy a meal while taking in the beautiful scenery.\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nOne of the best features of Orlando Premium Outlets is its convenient location. The shopping center is situated just off of Interstate 4, making it easy to access from anywhere in the Orlando area. Additionally, it\'s located just minutes from many of the city\'s top attractions, including the theme parks and downtown Orlando.\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nOverall, Orlando Premium Outlets is an incredible destination for visitors looking for a high-end shopping experience in a beautiful outdoor setting. With its wide range of stores, incredible discounts, and convenient location, this shopping center is a must-visit destination for anyone looking to indulge in some retail therapy during their time in Orlando. Whether you\'re a fashion enthusiast or just looking for a fun day out, Orlando Premium Outlets is the perfect destination for a memorable shopping experience in Orlando.\r\n\r\n', 'orlandooutlets/image1.jpeg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '4951 International Dr, Orlando, FL 32819', 'https://www.premiumoutlets.com/', '', '', 'Shop till you drop at Orlando International Premium Outlets! Discover incredible deals on designer brands like Coach, Nike, and Michael Kors. With over 180 stores, you\'ll find something for everyone. Plan your visit today and indulge in some retail therapy.', '$$', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'N', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', ''),
(49, 'Museum of Illusions Orlando', 'The Museum of Illusions Orlando is a must-visit attraction for anyone looking for a fun and interactive experience. This unique museum offers a range of optical illusions and exhibits that are designed to trick the senses and challenge your perception of reality.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nThe museum is divided into several themed rooms, each featuring its own set of illusions and interactive displays. Some of the most popular exhibits include the Infinity Room, which features a seemingly endless array of mirrors, and the Ames Room, which uses clever design techniques to create a mind-bending optical illusion.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nOne of the things that sets the Museum of Illusions apart from other museums is the level of interactivity it offers. Rather than simply viewing the exhibits, you can actually become a part of them. For example, in the Clone Room, you can pose for photos with your own \"clones\" that appear to be standing in different locations throughout the room.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nAnother popular feature of the museum is the Upside Down House, which is exactly what it sounds like. Here, you\'ll find a fully furnished house that has been built upside down, creating a disorienting and surreal experience that is sure to amaze and delight visitors of all ages.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nIn addition to the illusions themselves, the Museum of Illusions also offers a range of educational exhibits and interactive displays that provide interesting background information on the science behind the illusions. This makes it a great destination for school groups, families, and anyone who is interested in learning more about the fascinating world of perception and illusion.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nOverall, the Museum of Illusions Orlando is a fun and exciting attraction that is sure to be a highlight of your trip to the area. So why not add it to your itinerary today and experience the magic of illusion for yourself?\r\n', 'museumofillusions/image1.jpeg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '8375 International Drive Icon Park, Suite #250, Orlando, FL 32819', 'https://moiorlando.com/', '', '', 'Experience the impossible at Museum of Illusions Orlando! Our mind-bending exhibits will challenge your perceptions and leave you amazed. From optical illusions to holograms, there\'s something for everyone. Book your tickets today and get ready for an unforgettable adventure.', '24.99', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'Y', 'N', ''),
(50, 'Orlando Science Center', 'Orlando Science Center is the perfect destination for families, science enthusiasts, and anyone looking for an interactive and educational experience. With four floors of exhibits, there is something for everyone to enjoy.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nStart your journey at the “Our Planet” exhibit, where you can learn about Earth\'s diverse ecosystems, conservation efforts, and ways to help protect our planet. Explore the “DinoDigs” exhibit and discover the history of dinosaurs through fossils and interactive displays. Check out the “Fusion: A STEAM Gallery” exhibit, where art and science collide, and create your own masterpiece using technology and traditional art supplies.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nOne of the highlights of the museum is the Crosby Observatory, which offers visitors the opportunity to gaze at the stars using a variety of telescopes. The observatory is home to one of the largest publicly accessible telescopes in Florida, making it a must-visit attraction for astronomy enthusiasts.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nThe Orlando Science Center also features a variety of hands-on activities for visitors of all ages. In the “Kinetic Zone” exhibit, you can experiment with physics principles and engineering concepts through interactive displays and games. In the “KidsTown” exhibit, young children can explore and learn through imaginative play in a child-sized town.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nFor those looking to experience something truly unique, the Orlando Science Center offers a variety of immersive experiences in their Digital Adventure Theater. From 3D movies to planetarium shows, these experiences will transport you to new worlds and leave you with a newfound appreciation for the wonders of the universe.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nDon\'t forget to check out the museum\'s schedule of special events and traveling exhibits, which change throughout the year. With so much to see and do, the Orlando Science Center is a must-visit destination for anyone looking for an interactive and educational experience.\r\n', 'orlandosciencecenter/image1.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '777 E Princeton St, Orlando, FL 32803', 'https://www.osc.org/', '', '', 'Discover science like never before at Orlando Science Center! With interactive exhibits and hands-on displays, you\'ll be amazed at the wonders of the cosmos and the human body. Book your tickets now for an unforgettable educational adventure.', '24.00', 'M,T,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', ''),
(51, 'Titanic: The Artifact Exhibition', 'Titanic: The Artifact Exhibition is a must-see attraction for anyone interested in the history of the Titanic and the stories of the passengers who were aboard the ship. Located in Orlando, Florida, this exhibition is a unique and immersive experience that transports visitors back in time to the fateful night of April 14, 1912.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nUpon entering the exhibition, visitors receive a replica boarding pass of an actual passenger who was aboard the Titanic. Throughout the exhibition, they can learn about the lives of the passengers and crew members, the ship\'s design and construction, and the events leading up to its tragic sinking. The exhibition features over 300 artifacts recovered from the wreckage of the Titanic, including clothing, jewelry, personal belongings, and even a piece of the ship\'s hull.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nOne of the most compelling aspects of the exhibition is the opportunity to step inside recreations of the Titanic\'s cabins and other areas of the ship. Visitors can see what life was like for passengers traveling in first, second, and third class, and experience the grandeur of the Titanic\'s public spaces, such as the grand staircase and the first-class lounge.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nIn addition to the exhibition itself, visitors can also attend special events and programs, such as lectures from Titanic experts and historians, or even a guided tour of the exhibition led by a costumed actor portraying one of the Titanic\'s passengers or crew members.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nOverall, Titanic: The Artifact Exhibition is a fascinating and educational experience that appeals to visitors of all ages. Whether you\'re a history buff or simply curious about one of the most famous maritime disasters in history, this exhibition is a must-visit attraction during your trip to Orlando.\r\n', 'titanic/image1.jpeg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '7324 International Dr, Orlando, FL 32819', 'https://titanicorlando.com/', '', '', 'Explore the tragic story of the Titanic and its passengers through a captivating exhibit featuring authentic artifacts recovered from the wreckage.', '23.95', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'Y', 'N', ''),
(52, 'Ripley\'s Believe It or Not!', 'If you\'re looking for a unique and bizarre experience in Orlando, Ripley\'s Believe It or Not! should definitely be on your list. This world-renowned attraction is filled with oddities and curiosities from all over the world, making it the perfect place to spend a few hours of your day.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nOne of the highlights of Ripley\'s Believe It or Not! is the collection of shrunken heads, which is said to be one of the largest in the world. You can also explore an authentic vampire killing kit, see a portrait of Marilyn Monroe made entirely out of candy, and marvel at a replica of the world\'s tallest man.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nThe museum also has a variety of interactive exhibits that will challenge your senses and perception, such as the spinning vortex tunnel and the mirror maze. There are also plenty of hands-on exhibits that will keep both adults and children entertained for hours, including a 19-foot-tall Transformer made entirely out of car parts and a life-size statue of the world\'s heaviest man.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nIn addition to the exhibits, Ripley\'s Believe It or Not! offers a variety of live shows and performances throughout the day. You can witness amazing stunts and feats of strength, or get up close and personal with some of the museum\'s most fascinating artifacts.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nOverall, Ripley\'s Believe It or Not! is a must-visit attraction for anyone who wants to experience something truly unique and memorable in Orlando. Whether you\'re a fan of the bizarre and macabre, or just want to have some fun with your family and friends, this museum is sure to leave a lasting impression on you.\r\n', 'ripley/image1.jpeg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '8201 International Dr, Orlando, FL 32819', 'https://www.ripleys.com/orlando/', '', '', 'Experience the weird, wacky and wonderful world of Ripley\'s Believe It or Not! in Orlando, with over 16 galleries filled with incredible artifacts and interactive exhibits.', '27.99', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'Y', 'N', '');
