(53, 'Sleuths Mystery Dinner Shows', 'Sleuths Mystery Dinner Shows is an immersive and interactive dining experience that will transport you to a world of mystery, intrigue, and suspense. Located in the heart of Orlando\'s International Drive, this popular attraction offers an evening of delicious food, drinks, and entertainment that you won\'t soon forget.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nThe show begins as soon as you arrive, with a cast of talented actors greeting you and setting the stage for the evening\'s events. As you settle into your seat and enjoy a drink from the fully stocked bar, you\'ll start to piece together the clues and try to solve the mystery at the heart of the show.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nThe menu features a variety of delicious options, including chicken, beef, fish, and vegetarian dishes, so there\'s something for everyone. All meals include a salad, bread, and dessert, as well as coffee, tea, and soft drinks.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nThroughout the show, the actors will engage with the audience, offering hints and clues to help you solve the mystery. You\'ll have the chance to ask questions, share your theories, and even participate in the action if you choose. With multiple shows each week, you can return again and again to try to solve a new mystery each time.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nSleuths Mystery Dinner Shows is a great choice for couples, families, and groups looking for a fun and unique night out. It\'s perfect for celebrating special occasions like birthdays, anniversaries, and bachelorette parties, as well as corporate events and team building activities.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nTickets can be purchased online or by phone, and it\'s recommended to book in advance as shows often sell out. With its mix of delicious food, exciting entertainment, and engaging audience participation, Sleuths Mystery Dinner Shows is a must-visit attraction in Orlando.\r\n', 'sleuths/image1.jpeg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '8267 International Dr, Orlando, FL 32819', 'https://www.sleuths.com/', '', '', 'Step into the world of mystery and intrigue with Sleuths Mystery Dinner Shows in Orlando, an interactive experience where you\'ll solve a crime while enjoying a delicious dinner.', '72.95', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', ''),
(54, 'Orlando Improv', 'Orlando Improv is the premier destination for comedy in Central Florida! Whether you’re a local or just visiting the area, Orlando Improv offers a one-of-a-kind entertainment experience that is sure to leave you laughing.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nAs part of the renowned Improv Comedy Club franchise, our venue has hosted some of the biggest names in comedy, from Kevin Hart to Jerry Seinfeld. We pride ourselves on bringing the best talent to our stage, offering a wide range of performances, including stand-up, sketch comedy, and improv.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nOur intimate venue provides a unique and immersive atmosphere that puts you right in the middle of the action. With seating for up to 300 guests, every seat in the house offers a great view of the stage. In addition to our regular performances, we also offer special events such as open mic nights, themed shows, and meet-and-greets with comedians.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nBut the entertainment doesn’t stop with the show. Our full-service bar offers a wide selection of drinks, including craft beers and signature cocktails. Whether you’re in the mood for a classic margarita or a refreshing mojito, our experienced bartenders will craft the perfect drink to complement your night of laughs.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nOrlando Improv is conveniently located in Pointe Orlando, a premier dining and entertainment district in the heart of International Drive. With plenty of nearby restaurants and attractions, it’s easy to make a night out of your visit to our comedy club.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nTickets for our shows can be purchased online or at the box office. We offer reserved seating, so you can choose the perfect spot to enjoy the show. For groups or special events, we also offer private rentals of our venue.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nIf you’re looking for a night of laughter and entertainment, look no further than Orlando Improv. Our talented comedians and welcoming atmosphere make us the perfect choice for a fun night out with friends or a memorable date night.\r\n', 'orlandoimprov/image1.jpeg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '9101 International Dr Suite 2310, Orlando, FL 32819', 'https://theimprovorlando.com/', '', '', 'Get ready to laugh until it hurts at Orlando Improv, a premier comedy club featuring nationally renowned comedians and a full bar menu for a night of non-stop entertainment.', '20.00', 'W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 21, 'Y', 'N', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', ''),
(55, 'Outta Control Dinner Show', 'Looking for a night full of laughter and entertainment in Orlando? Look no further than the Outta Control Dinner Show at WonderWorks!\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nThis interactive show is perfect for families and adults alike, with hilarious comedy and magic acts that will leave you amazed. The show takes place in a 250-seat theater where you\'ll be seated with other guests, creating a fun and lively atmosphere.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nThe experience starts with a delicious all-you-can-eat buffet featuring classic Italian-American dishes such as pizza, salad, and pasta. The buffet also includes unlimited beer, wine, and soda, making it the perfect place to kick back and relax after a day exploring Orlando\'s theme parks.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nOnce the show begins, you\'ll be entertained by Tony Brent, a master of improvisational comedy who will keep you laughing all night long. He\'ll also bring up members of the audience to participate in the show, making it an interactive experience that\'s different every time.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nIn addition to comedy, the show also features mind-bending magic acts that will have you scratching your head and wondering how it\'s possible. The show is family-friendly, so kids will be just as amazed as the adults.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nLocated in the heart of International Drive, the Outta Control Dinner Show is easy to get to and makes for a great evening out during your Orlando vacation. The theater is wheelchair accessible, and the show runs year-round with multiple showtimes available each day.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nTickets can be purchased online or at the door, but it\'s recommended to book in advance as shows can sell out quickly. So don\'t miss your chance to experience one of Orlando\'s most unique and entertaining dinner shows!\r\n', 'outtacontrol/image1.jpeg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '9067 International Dr, Orlando, FL 32819', 'https://www.wonderworksonline.com/orlando/the-experience/the-outta-control-magic-comedy-dinner-show/', '', '', 'Enjoy a hilarious and interactive experience at the Outta Control Dinner Show in Orlando, where you\'ll be amazed by magic, comedy, and unlimited pizza, salad, and drinks.', '34.99', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', ''),
(56, 'Orlando Magic', 'The Orlando Magic is a professional basketball team in the National Basketball Association (NBA), based in Orlando, Florida. Founded in 1989, the team has a rich history and loyal fan base that makes it a must-visit for sports fans.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nThe team plays at the Amway Center, a state-of-the-art arena that is a destination in itself. The arena has multiple levels of seating and luxury suites, as well as restaurants, bars, and lounges. The Amway Center is also home to the Orlando Magic Team Shop, where fans can purchase official team merchandise.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nIn addition to watching the games, fans can also take a behind-the-scenes tour of the Amway Center. The tour takes visitors through the arena\'s locker rooms, press conference rooms, and other exclusive areas that are not usually open to the public. Guests can also see the court up close and even take a shot on the hoop.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nThroughout the year, the Orlando Magic also hosts various events and activities for fans of all ages. This includes meet-and-greets with players and coaches, youth basketball clinics, and autograph sessions.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nFor those looking for the ultimate Orlando Magic experience, the team offers a variety of premium seating options. This includes courtside seats, luxury suites, and club seats that come with exclusive access to VIP lounges and amenities.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nAttending an Orlando Magic game is a fun and exciting way to spend an evening in Orlando. With a talented team, a beautiful arena, and plenty of fan activities, it\'s no wonder why the Magic have such a passionate following. Whether you\'re a die-hard basketball fan or just looking for a unique experience, an Orlando Magic game is definitely worth checking out.\r\n', 'orlandomagic/image1.jpeg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '400 W Church St Suite 200, Orlando, FL 32801', 'https://www.nba.com/magic', '', '', 'Discover the magic of Orlando on your next travel adventure, home to the NBA\'s Orlando Magic and a world-famous destination for theme parks, entertainment, and family fun.', '20.00', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', ''),
(57, 'House of Blues Orlando', 'House of Blues Orlando is a premier entertainment venue that combines great music with Southern-inspired cuisine. Whether you\'re looking for a night out with friends or a unique date night experience, House of Blues Orlando has something for everyone.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nLocated in Disney Springs, House of Blues Orlando boasts a lively atmosphere that is perfect for music lovers. The venue hosts a variety of events including concerts, comedy shows, and even gospel brunches. With a capacity of up to 2,000 guests, House of Blues Orlando provides an intimate setting to experience some of the best musical acts from around the world.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nIn addition to its live music events, House of Blues Orlando is also known for its Southern-style cuisine. The menu features classic dishes like jambalaya, gumbo, and fried chicken, as well as some unique twists like the Voodoo Shrimp and the Bayou Burger. There are also vegetarian and gluten-free options available, ensuring that everyone can find something to enjoy.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nFor those looking for a more exclusive experience, House of Blues Orlando offers VIP seating options. These include private balcony seating with excellent views of the stage, a private bar, and access to a dedicated server. The VIP experience also includes early access to the venue and expedited entry, allowing you to skip the lines and get straight to the entertainment.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nFinally, House of Blues Orlando is also available for private events and corporate functions. The venue has multiple spaces available for rent, each with its own unique atmosphere and capacity. The expert events team at House of Blues Orlando can help you plan everything from a small, intimate gathering to a large, corporate conference.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nIn summary, House of Blues Orlando is the perfect destination for music lovers and foodies alike. With its lively atmosphere, world-class musical acts, and delicious Southern-style cuisine, House of Blues Orlando is sure to provide a memorable experience for all who visit.\r\n', 'houseofblues/image1.jpeg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '1490 E Buena Vista Dr, Orlando, FL 32830', 'https://www.houseofblues.com/orlando', '', '', 'Immerse yourself in the vibrant music scene of Orlando with a visit to House of Blues, featuring an eclectic mix of live performances, delicious Southern cuisine, and a unique atmosphere that captures the essence of the city\'s rich cultural heritage.', '40.50', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', ''),
(58, 'PopStroke', 'PopStroke is a unique entertainment destination located in Waterford, Florida. PopStroke offers visitors a chance to play mini-golf on beautiful courses designed by Tiger Woods, as well as enjoy delicious food and drinks in a fun and vibrant atmosphere.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nPopStroke features two 18-hole mini-golf courses designed by professional golfer Tiger Woods. The courses are beautifully landscaped and offer challenging and fun obstacles for players of all skill levels. Each hole is unique and features fun themes such as a lighthouse, a windmill, and a castle. Visitors can enjoy a round of mini-golf with friends and family while taking in the beautiful scenery and having a great time.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nPopStroke also features a restaurant and bar that offers delicious food and drinks. The menu features classic American dishes with a twist, such as chicken and waffles, loaded tater tots, and burgers. The bar offers a variety of craft beers, cocktails, and wines that pair perfectly with the food. Visitors can enjoy their meals on the outdoor patio or in the air-conditioned dining room while watching sports on the big screen TVs.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nPopStroke is not just a mini-golf course and restaurant, it\'s a destination that offers a fun and vibrant atmosphere. The outdoor patio is decorated with colorful furniture, bright umbrellas, and fun games such as cornhole and giant Jenga. Visitors can also take advantage of the photo booth and take memorable pictures with friends and family. The staff is friendly and welcoming, adding to the overall positive experience.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nPopStroke is open seven days a week from 11am to 10pm. The mini-golf course is $24 for adults and $19 for children under 12. Visitors can also enjoy food and drinks at the restaurant and bar, with prices ranging from $5 to $16. PopStroke is a family-friendly destination and welcomes visitors of all ages. Visitors should plan to wear comfortable clothing and shoes, and bring sunscreen and sunglasses for the outdoor patio.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nIn conclusion, PopStroke is a unique and fun destination that offers visitors a chance to play mini-golf on beautiful courses designed by Tiger Woods, enjoy delicious food and drinks, and soak up the fun and vibrant atmosphere. With its friendly staff, memorable photo opportunities, and exciting games, PopStroke is a must-visit destination for families and friends looking for a fun and entertaining day out.\r\n\r\n', 'popstroke/image1.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '321 N Alafaya Trail, Orlando, FL 32828', 'https://popstroke.com/orlando-waterford-lakes/', '', '', 'Experience the ultimate family-friendly entertainment destination at PopStroke in Waterford, featuring exciting mini-golf courses, delicious food and drinks, and an inviting atmosphere that\'s perfect for all ages.', '25.00', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'N', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', ''),
(59, 'Harry P Leu Gardens', 'Harry P Leu Gardens is a beautiful and peaceful oasis in the heart of Orlando, Florida. With its stunning gardens, historical home, and educational programs, Harry P Leu Gardens is the perfect destination for nature lovers and history buffs alike.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nHarry P Leu Gardens features 50 acres of beautifully landscaped gardens that showcase a variety of flora and fauna. Visitors can explore themed gardens such as the Rose Garden, the Idea Garden, and the Butterfly Garden. The gardens also feature a variety of exotic plants, including bamboo, cycads, and ferns. Visitors can take a leisurely stroll along the meandering paths and enjoy the peaceful surroundings.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nThe gardens are home to the Leu House Museum, a historical home that dates back to the 19th century. Visitors can take a guided tour of the house and learn about its history and architecture. The house is decorated with antique furniture and features original artwork, providing a glimpse into the past. Visitors can also learn about the life of the Leu family, who were instrumental in the development of Orlando.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nHarry P Leu Gardens offers a variety of educational programs for visitors of all ages. The gardens host workshops and classes on gardening, horticulture, and sustainability. Visitors can also participate in guided tours and nature walks led by knowledgeable staff. The gardens also offer programs for children, such as the Junior Gardeners program, which teaches kids about the importance of gardening and the environment.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nHarry P Leu Gardens is open seven days a week from 9am to 5pm. Admission is $10 for adults and $5 for children aged 4-17. Children under 4 are free. The gardens are wheelchair accessible, and visitors can rent wheelchairs and strollers if needed. Visitors should wear comfortable shoes and bring sunscreen and a hat for the outdoor areas. The gardens also have a gift shop and a café that serves light refreshments.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nIn conclusion, Harry P Leu Gardens is a beautiful and educational destination that offers visitors a chance to explore stunning gardens, learn about the history of Orlando, and participate in educational programs. With its peaceful surroundings, historical home, and variety of activities, Harry P Leu Gardens is a must-visit destination for nature lovers, history buffs, and families looking for a relaxing and informative day out.\r\n', 'harrypleu/image1.jpeg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '1920 N Forest Ave, Orlando, FL 32803', 'https://www.leugardens.org/', '', '', 'Escape to the natural beauty and tranquility of Harry P Leu Gardens in Orlando, where you can explore a stunning collection of tropical plants and flowers, relax in peaceful gardens, and learn about the history and culture of this enchanting city.', '15.00', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'N', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', 'N', ''),
(60, 'The Mall at Millenia', 'The Mall at Millenia is a world-class shopping destination located in the heart of Orlando, Florida. With over 150 high-end stores and luxury brands, this upscale shopping center is a must-visit for fashion lovers and shopping enthusiasts.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nFrom fashion-forward clothing and accessories to luxurious home décor and furnishings, The Mall at Millenia has something for everyone. High-end brands such as Chanel, Gucci, Louis Vuitton, Prada, and Versace can be found in this luxurious shopping center, as well as popular department stores such as Macy\'s and Neiman Marcus.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nIn addition to shopping, The Mall at Millenia also offers an array of dining options, ranging from casual eateries to fine dining restaurants. Some of the most popular dining destinations include The Cheesecake Factory, Brio Tuscan Grille, and The Capital Grille.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nAside from shopping and dining, The Mall at Millenia also hosts several events and activities throughout the year. From fashion shows and art exhibits to live music performances and holiday celebrations, there\'s always something happening at this premier shopping destination.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nFor visitors who want to make the most of their shopping experience, The Mall at Millenia offers a range of amenities and services. Complimentary Wi-Fi is available throughout the mall, and guests can also take advantage of valet parking and personal shopping services. The mall also features a guest services center where visitors can get information on events, store locations, and other services.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nWhether you\'re looking for the latest designer fashions or simply want to indulge in a little retail therapy, The Mall at Millenia is the perfect destination for luxury shopping and dining in Orlando. With its upscale atmosphere, wide range of high-end stores, and variety of amenities, this premier shopping center is a must-visit for anyone looking for an unforgettable shopping experience.\r\n', 'milleniamall/image1.jpeg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '4200 Conroy Rd, Orlando, FL 32839', 'https://www.mallatmillenia.com/', '', '', 'Discover luxury shopping at The Mall at Millenia, one of Orlando\'s premier destinations, featuring designer brands, restaurants, and entertainment.', '$$', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', ''),
(61, 'The Florida Mall', 'The Florida Mall is a shopper\'s paradise and one of the largest malls in Central Florida, featuring more than 250 stores, restaurants, and entertainment options. Located just minutes from Orlando International Airport and a short drive from the popular theme parks, The Florida Mall is a must-visit destination for any shopping enthusiast.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nSpanning over 1.8 million square feet, the mall boasts a diverse range of retailers including high-end brands such as Louis Vuitton, Gucci, and Prada, as well as popular department stores like Macy\'s, Nordstrom, and Dillard\'s. With a variety of shopping experiences, The Florida Mall offers something for everyone from luxury shopping to bargain hunting.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nFor those looking for a break from shopping, The Florida Mall offers a range of dining options to satisfy any appetite. With over 30 dining options, visitors can choose from a variety of cuisines including American, Italian, Japanese, and Mexican, to name a few. Whether it\'s a quick snack or a sit-down meal, there is something for every taste.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nAside from shopping and dining, The Florida Mall also offers a variety of entertainment options. The Crayola Experience is a popular attraction for families with young children, providing interactive activities and hands-on exhibits. Visitors can also catch a movie at the on-site Cinemark Theater or enjoy a game of bowling at the StrikeOuts Bowling Center.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nIn addition to its wide range of shopping, dining, and entertainment options, The Florida Mall also offers various services such as a concierge desk, currency exchange, and valet parking. The mall also offers a free shuttle service to select hotels in the area, making it easy and convenient for visitors to shop to their heart\'s content.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nWith its wide variety of offerings and convenient location, The Florida Mall is a must-visit destination for any traveler looking for a shopping experience in Orlando.\r\n', 'floridamall/image1.jpeg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '8001 S Orange Blossom Trl, Orlando, FL 32809', 'https://www.simon.com/mall/the-florida-mall', '', '', 'Shop until you drop at The Florida Mall in Orlando, with over 250 stores featuring fashion, electronics, and luxury goods, along with dining options to satisfy all cravings. ', '$$', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', ''),
(62, 'Clearwater Beach', 'Clearwater Beach is a popular destination on the west coast of Florida, known for its stunning white sand beaches, crystal-clear waters, and endless activities for visitors of all ages. Located just a short drive from Tampa and St. Petersburg, Clearwater Beach offers a perfect getaway for those seeking sun, sand, and fun.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nOne of the main attractions of Clearwater Beach is its pristine beaches. The soft, powdery sand stretches for miles, and the calm Gulf of Mexico waters offer the perfect conditions for swimming, sunbathing, and water sports. Visitors can rent jet skis, paddleboards, and kayaks to explore the surrounding waters, or take a sunset sailboat cruise for a more relaxing experience.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nIn addition to its beaches, Clearwater Beach is home to a variety of other attractions. The Clearwater Marine Aquarium is a must-visit for families, featuring dolphins, sea turtles, and other marine life. The Pier 60 area is a popular gathering spot for street performers, artisans, and musicians, and hosts daily sunset celebrations with live music and food vendors. Visitors can also take a dolphin-watching cruise or a deep-sea fishing excursion to catch some of the Gulf\'s most sought-after fish.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nFor those looking to escape the sun, Clearwater Beach has a number of indoor attractions as well. The nearby city of Clearwater boasts a variety of museums, including the Dunedin Fine Art Center and the Clearwater Historical Society. The area is also home to a number of shopping and dining options, with everything from quaint beachfront cafes to upscale restaurants.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nWith its picturesque beaches, family-friendly attractions, and variety of activities, Clearwater Beach is a must-visit destination for anyone looking to experience the beauty of Florida\'s Gulf coast. Whether you\'re looking for relaxation, adventure, or a little bit of both, Clearwater Beach has something for everyone.\r\n', 'clearwaterbeach/image1.jpeg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Clearwater Beach, Clearwater, FL', 'https://www.visitstpeteclearwater.com/communities/clearwater-beach', '', '', 'Clearwater Beach, located on the Gulf of Mexico, is a stunning destination for those looking for a relaxing beach vacation with crystal clear waters, white sandy beaches, and plenty of water activities for all ages.', '0', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'N', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', ''),
(63, 'Dr. Phillips Center for the Performing Arts', 'The Dr. Phillips Center for the Performing Arts is a world-class performing arts venue located in the heart of downtown Orlando, Florida. It is a must-see destination for visitors who appreciate the performing arts and want to experience the best of live entertainment in Orlando.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nThe center hosts a wide range of performances, from Broadway shows and musicals to ballet and opera, as well as concerts and comedy shows. With three distinct theaters, including the Walt Disney Theater, the Alexis & Jim Pugh Theater, and the smaller, more intimate DeVos Family Room, there is something for everyone at the Dr. Phillips Center. The theaters feature state-of-the-art sound and lighting systems and offer excellent acoustics, providing an unforgettable experience for audiences.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nIn addition to its outstanding performances, the Dr. Phillips Center also offers a variety of educational programs and community outreach initiatives. These programs aim to promote arts education and inspire the next generation of performers, artists, and arts lovers. The center also hosts events and activities throughout the year, including art exhibits, festivals, and more.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nVisitors can make the most of their visit by taking advantage of the many amenities and services available at the center. These include on-site dining options, such as the laid-back 9th Street Kitchen and the more upscale Arts Café, as well as a gift shop where visitors can purchase souvenirs and other items.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nWhether you are a seasoned theater-goer or simply looking for a fun and unique experience, the Dr. Phillips Center for the Performing Arts is a must-visit destination in Orlando. With its world-class performances, outstanding facilities, and commitment to promoting the arts, it is sure to leave a lasting impression on visitors of all ages.\r\n', 'dpac/image1.jpeg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '445 S Magnolia Ave, Orlando, FL 32801', 'https://www.drphillipscenter.org/', '', '', 'Experience the vibrant arts and cultural scene of Orlando at the Dr. Phillips Center for the Performing Arts, where world-class performers take center stage and awe-inspiring performances leave a lasting impression on visitors.', '$$', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 0, 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', ''),
(64, 'Orlando Repertory Theatre', 'Orlando Repertory Theatre is where the magic of live theatre comes to life! Located in the heart of Orlando, this nationally recognized theatre is a must-visit for anyone looking for an unforgettable cultural experience.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nWith a mission to create and produce professional theatre productions for all ages, the Orlando Repertory Theatre offers a diverse lineup of shows throughout the year. From classic tales like The Cat in the Hat and The Little Mermaid to modern works like The Diary of Anne Frank and The Best Christmas Pageant Ever, there\'s something for everyone to enjoy.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nOne of the unique features of the Orlando Repertory Theatre is their commitment to producing theatre specifically for young audiences. Their Youth Academy program offers classes, workshops, and camps for children and teenagers, providing them with opportunities to develop their skills and explore their creativity.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nThe theatre is also dedicated to accessibility, offering ASL interpreted performances, sensory-friendly shows, and audio-described performances for the visually impaired. Plus, their \"Pay What You Wish\" performances allow audiences to experience the magic of live theatre regardless of their financial circumstances.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nIn addition to the incredible productions, the Orlando Repertory Theatre also features a range of special events throughout the year, including behind-the-scenes tours, pre-show discussions, and meet-and-greets with the cast and crew.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nIf you\'re planning a trip to Orlando, be sure to check out the Orlando Repertory Theatre\'s upcoming shows and events. With their commitment to education, accessibility, and high-quality theatre productions, it\'s no wonder that they are a beloved institution in the local arts community.\r\n', 'orlandorepertory/image1.jpeg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '1001 E Princeton St, Orlando, FL 32803', 'https://www.orlandorep.com/', '', '', 'Experience world-class theater productions for all ages at the Orlando Repertory Theatre, a premier performing arts center located in the heart of Orlando, Florida.', '$', 'M,T,W,Th,F', 0, 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', ''),
(65, 'The Plaza Live', 'The Plaza Live is a historic live music venue in Orlando, Florida. Originally opened in 1963 as a cinema, it was converted into a concert hall in the 1990s and has since become a beloved destination for music fans.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nThe Plaza Live hosts a variety of acts from various genres, including rock, pop, jazz, and classical music. The intimate space allows for a unique and engaging concert experience, with audiences often describing the venue as having excellent acoustics and great sightlines from every seat.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nThe venue has a capacity of just over 1,000, which makes for an intimate setting that is ideal for smaller shows and more up-close performances. It has a full bar on-site and offers VIP packages for those who want to take their concert experience to the next level.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nIn addition to its impressive lineup of music acts, The Plaza Live also hosts a range of other events, including comedy shows, theatrical performances, and private events. Its location in the heart of Orlando makes it easily accessible from all areas of the city.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nVisitors to The Plaza Live can enjoy a night out on the town, with plenty of dining and entertainment options nearby. There are also several hotels in the area, making it easy to plan a trip to Orlando specifically to see a show at the venue.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nWhether you\'re a music aficionado or simply looking for a unique night out in Orlando, The Plaza Live is a must-visit destination. Check out their calendar of events to see who\'s playing next, and book your tickets today to experience the magic of this historic venue for yourself.\r\n', 'theplaza/image1.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '425 N Bumby Ave, Orlando, FL 32803', 'https://www.plazaliveorlando.org/', '', '', 'Discover the vibrant Orlando music scene with The Plaza Live, a historic venue featuring a diverse lineup of concerts and events, sure to satisfy any music lover\'s appetite. ', '$$$', 'M,T,W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 18, 'Y', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', ''),
(66, 'The Social', 'The Social is one of the most renowned live music venues in Orlando, Florida. Located in the heart of the city\'s downtown area, it has been the go-to destination for music lovers since its inception in 2000.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nThe venue boasts a state-of-the-art sound system, ensuring that every performance is crystal clear and of the highest quality. With a capacity of 450, the intimate setting provides a unique experience for both fans and performers. The Social has hosted a variety of genres, including rock, hip hop, electronic, and indie music. It has featured performances by big names such as The Black Keys, Arctic Monkeys, The Lumineers, and many more.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nIn addition to live music, The Social also hosts events such as comedy shows, film screenings, and themed parties. The venue has a full bar, offering a wide selection of beers, wines, and cocktails. It also serves tasty bites, including pizza, nachos, and other bar favorites.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nThe atmosphere at The Social is casual and laid back, providing a perfect spot to hang out with friends and enjoy great music. The venue has a cozy interior, with exposed brick walls and vintage decor. The outdoor patio provides a great spot to relax between sets or enjoy a drink on a beautiful Florida evening.\r\n\r\n<br><br> \r\n\r\nIf you\'re planning a trip to Orlando and want to experience the city\'s vibrant music scene, The Social is a must-visit destination. With its eclectic lineup of performers and intimate setting, it provides a unique and memorable experience for visitors and locals alike. Check out their calendar of events and plan your visit to catch your favorite artist or discover new talent.\r\n', 'thesocial/image1.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '54 N Orange Ave, Orlando, FL 32801', 'https://www.beachamorlando.com/', '', '', 'The Social is a premier downtown venue that hosts a wide range of musical acts, from up-and-coming local bands to internationally acclaimed artists, in an intimate and vibrant setting.', '$$$', 'W,Th,F,Sa,Su', 18, 'Y', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', '');
